(103, 10, '转发教务处通知-网上退补选相关安排', '', NULL, 0, '详见附件内容！请同学们遵照通知内的时间安排并请相互转告，谢谢！', 942, 1234945705, '2009-02-18 00:28:25', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(104, 11, '2008年学院学生工作盘点', '', NULL, 0, '<IMG style="WIDTH: 595px; HEIGHT: 403px" alt="" hspace=0 src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=44" align=baseline border=0><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=43" align=baseline border=0><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 长期以来，我院坚持以学风建设为龙头，积极引导学生勤奋学习,勇于创新,树立正确的人生目标, 并以坚强的意志努力拼搏。回顾08年的风雨兼程，我院学生工作取得长足进步和优异的成绩，获得了学校的好评。这是支年轻且人数不多的队伍，面对的却是各类的学生和各种繁琐的工作。对于这些，学生工作的同志一直探索着向前发展，虽然年轻，却有满腔的热情和爱心，努力把学生引导上成才的道路，探索和掌握学生个人和思想发展的规律。辅导员这支队伍在茁壮成长，面对再大再多的困难都可以过去，因为学生的安全和发展才是最重要的。身为人师，指引着学生思想的发展，塑造他们的灵魂，收获学生给予的奇迹。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 04级读研率：41.38%，居全校第六；<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 05级保研率：24%，居全校第一；<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 06级六级通过率：61.5%，居全校第五；<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 07级四级通过率：94.6%，居全校第四；<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 学生会获得最佳组织学生会称号；<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 钟霄获全国大学生英语竞赛一等奖；<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 25101010、25102020获校优秀班集体；<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 26102020获创优先进班集体；27102010获学业成绩典范班；<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 成电杯篮球赛中荣获亚军；校运会获得最佳通讯三等奖；<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 新生辩论赛中进入前四强； <BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 罗象宏荣获十大“成电杰出学生”称号<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 荆燕飞同学获“百人会”奖<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 刘洋――四川省抗震救灾大学生志愿者服务先进个人<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 石立群、刘今杰――成都市暑期“三下乡”社会实践活动优秀个人 <BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 邓鑫――校暑期“三下乡”社会实践活动优秀学生<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 叶谱英――四川省优秀共产党员<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 党员的奖学金获奖比例为：67.1%；四级通过率是100%；六级通过率是70.6%<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 按照学校在科技竞赛方面希望各个学院有标志性活动的要求，我们坚持推动素质教育，尤其是克服各种困难推动着我校“大学生程序设计竞赛”工作。今年，在校教务处的支持下，成功举办了“第六届程序设计大赛暨西南地区ACM邀请赛”，由去年168个队到今年的211支队476人参加，我院50人参赛、5支队15人获奖。同时取得2008四川省程序设计竞赛一等奖1名，二等奖3名和三等奖1名，以及最佳组织奖的可喜成绩。强化暑期集训、日常训练和每周论坛，组队参加第33届ACM/ICPC亚洲区预选赛，获得两银、五铜的成绩。带队赴加拿大参加ACM/ICPC世界总决赛，与清华、北大等共14所国内高校以及东京大学、首尔国立大学、德黑兰大学等世界名校一起同场竞技。在与从全世界6个大洲1821所大学6700余支队伍，通过网络赛和区域赛，最后胜出的97支队的高压比赛中，最后取得第31名，国内并列第六的优异成绩，为学校赢得了荣誉。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 为此，学院的学生工作受到了学校的好评，研究生科长刘燕辅导员被研究生院评为先进个人，本科辅导员叶谱英都被评为2008年度校优秀辅导员。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 新的一年开始了，也孕育着新的希望，相信09年我院学生工作会继续获得丰收。 ', 895, 1235096152, '2009-02-19 18:15:52', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(105, 10, '微积分习题课、答疑安排表', '', NULL, 0, '<P>各位老师及同学们：</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 本学期《微积分》课程的习题课、答疑安排请见附表！请相互转告，谢谢！</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>', 930, 1235304224, '2009-02-22 04:03:44', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(106, 12, '关于技术创新方法TRIZ理论讲座的通知', '', NULL, 0, '<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 党的十七大报告中，胡锦涛总书记高瞻远瞩地提出了“提高自主创新能力，建设创新型国家”的宏伟目标，并把它定位于国家发展战略的核心、提高综合国力的关键。为了实现创新，创新方法的普及应该走在前面。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;由科技处、研究生院、科技委主办一期为期5次课，10个学时的创新方法（TRIZ）讲座，系统地学习TRIZ理论，以便在实际的问题解决过程中应用创新方法、理论，实现高效地创新和发明。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;讲座时间：2月25、26、27号以及3月2、3号晚上7：30~9：30，地点：沙河校区一教104（其中26号在204室）。</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 欢迎各位老师、研究生积极参加！</P>', 995, 1235376069, '2009-02-23 00:01:09', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(107, 12, '关于联合自然基金申请的通知', '', NULL, 0, '&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 近期国家自然科学基金委网站陆续公布了"中澳科技合作特别基金",中国与俄罗斯双边研讨会项目、中国与俄罗斯合作研究项目等申报通知，请大家积极申报。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 近期为国家自然科学基金的集中申报期，基金委网站将陆续公布一些项目的申报通知和指南，请大家多留意。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 基金委主页<A href="http://www.nsfc.gov.cn">www.nsfc.gov.cn</A>', 969, 1235376411, '2009-02-23 00:06:51', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(108, 22, '      关于硕博连读网上报名的通知', '', NULL, 0, '<FONT face=宋体></FONT>', 1259, 1235378556, '2009-02-23 00:42:36', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(109, 11, '华尔街杂志发文称“数学家在美国是最好的职业”', '', NULL, 0, '<P>华尔街杂志发文称“数学家在美国是最好的职业”<BR>来源: 中国数学会, <A href="http://www.cms.org.cn/">http://www.cms.org.cn/</A></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在2009年1月6日出版的华尔街杂志上，发表了一篇题为“学数学以找到好的工作”的文章（Doing the Math to Find the Good Jobs）。该文称数学家列在美国最好职业榜第一位，保险精算师和统计学家分列第二和第三位。这个排行榜是由CareerCast.com制作的。主要参考了工作环境，收入，就业前景，体力要求，和强度。此项研究称一个数学家的平均工资是94,160美元，而伐木工人列在200项工作的最后。 以下是这个（最好最坏）排行榜前二十位和后二十位的工作。</P>\r\n<P>The Best and Worst Jobs</P>\r\n<P>The Best<BR>1. Mathematician<BR>2. Actuary<BR>3. Statistician<BR>4. Biologist<BR>5. Software Engineer<BR>6. Computer Systems Analyst<BR>7. Historian<BR>8. Sociologist<BR>9. Industrial Designer<BR>10. Accountant<BR>11. Economist<BR>12. Philosopher<BR>13. Physicist<BR>14. Parole Officer<BR>15. Meteorologist<BR>16. Medical Laboratory Technician<BR>17. Paralegal Assistant<BR>18. Computer Programmer<BR>19. Motion Picture Editor<BR>20. Astronomer</P>\r\n<P>The Worst</P>\r\n<P>200. Lumberjack <BR>199. Dairy Farmer <BR>198. Taxi Driver<BR>197. Seaman<BR>196. EMT <BR>195. Roofer <BR>194. Garbage Collector<BR>193. Welder<BR>192. Roustabout <BR>191. Ironworker <BR>190. Construction Worker<BR>189. Mail Carrier<BR>188. Sheet Metal Worker<BR>187. Auto Mechanic<BR>186. Butcher<BR>185. Nuclear Decontamination Tech<BR>184. Nurse (LN)<BR>183. Painter<BR>182. Child Care Worker<BR>181. Firefighter</P>', 1032, 1235438856, '2009-02-23 17:27:36', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(110, 13, '关于选派骨干教师暑期赴美国英语培训的通知', '', NULL, 0, '<SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 13.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN><STRONG>校内有关单位：<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">为进一步提高骨干教师双语教学和国际学术交流能力，学校决定继续开展选派骨干教师暑期赴美进行英语培训的工作，现将具体事宜通知如下：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN><STRONG>一、选派名额<o:p></o:p></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">按照国家外交部、国家外专家局对公派出国进修培训规模的新要求，选派总名额不超过<SPAN lang=EN-US>20</SPAN>名。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN><STRONG>二、选派对象<o:p></o:p></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">应为思想工作表现良好，并有一定英语基础的一线骨干教师。近五年曾参加过学校组织的赴澳、英、美进行英语培训（含英语教师的教学培训）的，本次原则上不再选派。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN><STRONG>三、培训时间和地点<o:p></o:p></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">2009</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">年<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>月中旬<SPAN lang=EN-US>―8</SPAN>月下旬（共<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>周），美国东海岸城市。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN><STRONG>四、培训内容<o:p></o:p></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">以语言培训为主，学术报告、科研和教学管理讲座为辅。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN><STRONG>五、培训费用<o:p></o:p></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">合计约<SPAN lang=EN-US>4.5</SPAN>万元，学校和教师各承担<SPAN lang=EN-US>1/2</SPAN>，<SPAN style="COLOR: red"><STRONG>（学院按教师承担额的<SPAN lang=EN-US>1/3</SPAN>提供资助）<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></STRONG></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN><STRONG>六、报名程序<o:p></o:p></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">被推荐人填写《赴美英语培训申请表》（可在资料下载栏目下载），由所在单位于<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>26</SPAN>日前将人员名单和《申请表》报人事处师资办公室<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN><STRONG><FONT color=#ff0000>注意：</FONT><FONT color=#0000ff>1.学院报名时间截止时间到<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>24</SPAN>日（星期二）止<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>\r\n<P><STRONG><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</SPAN>2.</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: blue; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">报名地点：主楼东<SPAN lang=EN-US>208</SPAN>室<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></STRONG></SPAN></P>', 917, 1235441110, '2009-02-23 18:05:10', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `article` (`articleid`, `sortid`, `title`, `source`, `author`, `userid`, `content`, `click`, `publish_time`, `launch_time`, `imageid`, `keyword1`, `keyword2`, `keyword3`) VALUES
(111, 13, '转发人事处―关于调整省本级城镇职工基本医疗保险待遇有关问题的通知', '', NULL, 0, '<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt 4.5pt 4.5pt 0cm; TEXT-INDENT: 120pt; mso-char-indent-count: 10.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">川劳社办〔<SPAN lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN>〕<SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>号<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">省本级各参保单位：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">为进一步完善城镇职工基本医疗保险制度，规范医疗保险管理，提高保障水平，经研究，现就调整省本级城镇职工基本医疗保险待遇有关问题通知如下：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">一、调整统筹基金起付标准</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">（一）基本医疗保险统筹基金的起付标准按定点医院级别确定和住院次数计算，具体标准调整为：三级医院<SPAN lang=EN-US>800</SPAN>元、二级医院<SPAN lang=EN-US>400</SPAN>元、一级医院<SPAN lang=EN-US>200</SPAN>元、定点社区卫生服务中心<SPAN lang=EN-US>160</SPAN>元，转外省医院<SPAN lang=EN-US>970</SPAN>元。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">（二）参保人员在一个自然年度内多次住院的，逐次降低<SPAN lang=EN-US>100</SPAN>元，但最低不低于<SPAN lang=EN-US>160</SPAN>元。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">（三）参保人员年满<SPAN lang=EN-US>90</SPAN>周岁及以上和患有精神病或艾滋病住院治疗的不计算统筹基金起付标准。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">（四）参保人员因恶性肿瘤手术及放化疗治疗，肾功能衰竭透析治疗及移植手术，慢性白血病、重型再生障碍性贫血、骨髓增生异常综合症、骨髓增生性疾病、系统性红斑狼疮治疗和肝、肾、骨髓（含造血干细胞）移植术后抗排异治疗需多次住院的，按照一个自然年度内只计算一次起付标准的原则处理，起付标准按参保人员首次住院治疗的医疗机构级别确定。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">（五）参保人员因病情需要，由低级别的定点医疗机构转往高级别的定点医疗机构，只补计统筹基金起付标准差额；由高级别定点医疗机构转往同级别或低级别综合医院或高级别定点医疗机构转往符合条件的社区卫生服务中心，不再另计统筹基金起付标准。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">二、调增统筹基金支付范围</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">调增下列医药费纳入基本医疗保险统筹基金的支付范围。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">（一）门诊抢救无效死亡发生的医药费用；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">（二）入院前<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>日内的阳性特殊门诊检查费用；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">具体支付管理办法，由省劳动保障部门另行制定。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">三、调整统筹基金支付比例</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">参保人员在定点医疗机构发生的符合规定的一次性住院费用，其数额在统筹基金起付标准以上、最高支付限额以下的部份，扣除个人首先支付的费用后，统筹基金的支付比例在现行报销水平（川劳社医［<SPAN lang=EN-US>2000</SPAN>］<SPAN lang=EN-US>27</SPAN>号）的基础上，对<SPAN lang=EN-US>50</SPAN>周岁至<SPAN lang=EN-US>59</SPAN>周岁的参保人员调增<SPAN lang=EN-US>2%</SPAN>，<SPAN lang=EN-US>60</SPAN>周岁至<SPAN lang=EN-US>69</SPAN>周岁的参保人员调增<SPAN lang=EN-US>4%</SPAN>，<SPAN lang=EN-US>70</SPAN>周岁至<SPAN lang=EN-US>79</SPAN>周岁的参保人员调增<SPAN lang=EN-US>6%</SPAN>，<SPAN lang=EN-US>80</SPAN>周岁及以上的参保人员调增<SPAN lang=EN-US>8%</SPAN>。根据年龄增加后的总支付比例不得超过<SPAN lang=EN-US>100%</SPAN>。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">四、调整个人账户支付范围</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">参保人员个人账户资金可以用于支付本人住院医疗费用个人负担部分（不含自费部分）。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">五、实行最低缴费年限和中断参保待遇支付</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">（一）<SPAN lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>日以后初次参加省本级城镇职工基本医疗保险的人员，连续缴费不得低于<SPAN lang=EN-US>15</SPAN>年（含原参保地缴费年限）。连续缴费达到最低缴费年限并同时达到法定退休年龄的，经主管部门审批办理退休手续、领取退休金（养老金）后，不再缴纳基本医疗保险费。连续缴费不足<SPAN lang=EN-US>15</SPAN>年，应按规定继续缴费或一次性补缴，使其连续缴费年限达到<SPAN lang=EN-US>15</SPAN>年。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">（二）参加省本级城镇职工基本医疗保险的人员、中断基本医疗保险关系<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>个月以上的，自重新参保之日起，连续缴费满<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>个月以后发生的住院医疗费用，统筹基金按规定予以支付，个人帐户从缴费当月起计入。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">六、实施时间</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">本通知从<SPAN lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>日开始实施。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: right; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=right><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;四川省劳动和社会保障厅<SPAN lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 4.5pt; TEXT-ALIGN: right; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</SPAN>四川省 财 政 厅<SPAN lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;二○○九年一月十九日</SPAN> ', 889, 1235441568, '2009-02-23 18:12:48', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(112, 13, '转发组织部―关于报送2009年度党员发展计划的通知', '', NULL, 0, '<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p><FONT size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">各党总支（直属党支部）、成都学院党委：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">为了进一步做好我校党员发展工作，切实保证新发展党员的质量，做到有领导、有计划地发展党员，请各单位认真贯彻执行“坚持标准，保证质量，改善结构，慎重发展”的党员发展方针，坚持“入党自愿和个别吸收”的原则，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">认真制定<SPAN lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN>年度党员发展计划，并按要求报送党委组织部。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">一、列入发展计划的对象要求<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">、入党积极分子要经过一年的教育和培养，方可列为发展对象。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">、发展对象必须是已经参加了我校党校培训，并顺利取得结业证书的入党积极分子；入校学习或来校工作前参加了其他单位（有党员发展审批权）组织的入党积极分子党校培训班的学习并顺利结业，有相应证明的入党积极分子。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">二、确定发展计划的基本原则<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">、实事求是原则。要从实际出发，充分考虑本单位入党积极分子的成熟状况，避免出现急于求成、突击发展的现象。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">、宏观指导原则。确定的发展数字是指导性的，要从宏观上保持适当的数量和合理的结构比例，注意加大青年教师发展党员的力度。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">、民主集中制原则。各党支部应召开党员大会，在充分讨论的基础上确定发展计划，报党总支审核（直属党支部直接报党委组织部审核）<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">三、报送发展计划的要求<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">、本次报送的党员发展计划以<SPAN lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN>年上半年的发展计划为主，综合考虑<SPAN lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN>年下半年的发展计划，各单位可以在<?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate w:st="on" Year="2009" Month="7" Day="1" IsLunarDate="False" IsROCDate="False"><SPAN lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>日</st1:chsdate>前对下半年发展计划根据实际情况做相应调整，并将下半年的发展对象名单报送党委组织部。党委组织部将依据发展对象名单审批有关党员发展材料，未列入名单人员材料将不予审批。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">、<FONT color=#ff0000><STRONG>请各单位于<st1:chsdate w:st="on" Year="2009" Month="2" Day="27" IsLunarDate="False" IsROCDate="False"><SPAN lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>25</SPAN>日</st1:chsdate>前</STRONG></FONT>，将填写完毕的<SPAN lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN>年度党员发展计划表（附件<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>）和上半年拟发展对象名单（附件<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>）报送党委组织部（加盖公章），同时将电子版<SPAN lang=EN-US><A href="mailto:zzb@uestc.edu.cn"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; text-underline: none"><SPAN lang=EN-US>发送至zzb@uestc.edu.cn</SPAN></SPAN></A></SPAN>。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">附件：<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>、<SPAN lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN>年度党员发展计划表<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">、<SPAN lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN>年上半年拟发展对象名单登记表<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: 288.0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><SPAN style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">党委组织部<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 1cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: 270.0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><SPAN style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><st1:chsdate w:st="on" Year="2008" Month="12" Day="22" IsLunarDate="False" IsROCDate="False">2008<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>年12</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>月22</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>日</SPAN></SPAN></st1:chsdate><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><BR>\r\n<P align=center></P>\r\n<P align=center>附件：<A style="CURSOR: hand" href="http://www.zzb.uestc.edu.cn/party/common/detail_down.php?file_id=368&amp;fid=2&amp;sid=0" target=_blank>[1]2009年党员发展计划</A>&nbsp;&nbsp;<BR>附件：<A style="CURSOR: hand" href="http://www.zzb.uestc.edu.cn/party/common/detail_down.php?file_id=369&amp;fid=2&amp;sid=0" target=_blank>[2]2009年上半年发展对象名单</A>&nbsp;&nbsp;<BR></P>', 1017, 1235442244, '2009-02-23 18:24:04', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(113, 13, '签领2008年目标责任制考核奖励经费', '', NULL, 0, '&nbsp; <SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 250%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">请各位老师<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="COLOR: red">于<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>25</SPAN>日之前</SPAN></B>到学院人事办来签领<SPAN lang=EN-US>2008</SPAN>年目标责任制考核奖励经费，请相互转告。 <SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 人事办</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2009-02-23<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 250%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left></SPAN></SPAN></P>', 983, 1235442723, '2009-02-23 18:32:03', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(115, 22, '   转发博士生报名通知', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 博士生报名通知</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>（</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>）通过硕博连读初选的，且准备参加</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">2007</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>年</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>月下旬硕博连读专题研究报告遴选的</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">2007</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>级硕士生，于</FONT></SPAN><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate w:st="on" IsROCDate="False" IsLunarDate="False" Day="1" Month="3" Year="2009"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>月</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>日</FONT></SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">--15</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>日要参加</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">2009</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">年博士生的入学报名（具体见研究生院招生办公室的通知）；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>（</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>）</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">2008</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>年和</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">2007</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>年获得优秀硕士学位论文的硕士生，拟准备攻读博士学位的，也要于</FONT></SPAN><st1:chsdate w:st="on" IsROCDate="False" IsLunarDate="False" Day="1" Month="3" Year="2009"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>月</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>日</FONT></SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">--15</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>日要参加</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">2009</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">年博士生的入学报名，并参加相应的入学考试（具体见研究生院招生办公室的通知），报名时请带上优秀硕士学位论文证书。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-FAMILY: Arial">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&n