sp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3. </FONT></SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">所学及报考专业为地球物理、地质、数学、物理、计算机、电子工程等相关理工类专业。</SPAN></B><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-alt: 13.5pt" align=center><FONT color=#333333><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">申请调剂的考生应认真阅读我所</SPAN></B><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">09</FONT></SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">年硕士</SPAN></B><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><A href="http://www.educity.cn/incsearch/search.asp?key=%D1%D0%BE%BF%C9%FA" target=_blank><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 15.0pt; mso-ansi-font-size: 15.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;"><SPAN lang=EN-US>研究生</SPAN></SPAN></A></SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 15pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">招生简