(202, 13, '转发―关于开展2009年春季教师资格认定工作的通知!', '', NULL, 0, '<TABLE class=MsoNormalTable style="MARGIN: auto auto auto -5.25pt; WIDTH: 104.3%; mso-cellspacing: 0cm; mso-padding-alt: 3.75pt 3.75pt 3.75pt 3.75pt" cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="104%" border=0>\r\n<TBODY>\r\n<TR style="mso-yfti-irow: 0; mso-yfti-firstrow: yes; mso-yfti-lastrow: yes">\r\n<TD style="BORDER-RIGHT: #ece9d8; PADDING-RIGHT: 3.75pt; BORDER-TOP: #ece9d8; PADDING-LEFT: 3.75pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 7.5pt; BORDER-LEFT: #ece9d8; WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-TOP: 7.5pt; BORDER-BOTTOM: #ece9d8; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent" width="100%">\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">校内各单位：</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">接四川省教育厅教师资格认定指导中心《关于开展<SPAN lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN>年春季教师资格认定的通知》（川教资<SPAN lang=EN-US>[2009]01</SPAN>号），现将我校春季教师资格认定工作的有关事宜通知如下：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">一、申请人员</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">我校在编在岗教师。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">二、时间安排</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>日至<SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>21</SPAN>日：网上报名。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">申请者登陆中国教师资格网（<U><SPAN lang=EN-US><A href="http://www.jszg.edu.cn/"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">www.jszg.edu.cn</SPAN></A></SPAN></U>），进入教师资格网上申报系统，并根据系统提示填写申请信息，认真核对。确认无误后提交，在线打印“报名号及现场确认信息”、《教师资格认定申请表》；下载《申请人思想品德鉴定表》，如实填写并打印。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>22</SPAN>日至<SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>30</SPAN>日：各单位审核申请者材料，并按以下时间统一报人事处师资办公室：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-highlight: yellow">4</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-highlight: yellow">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>28</SPAN>日：</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">自动化、机电、生命、<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">数学</SPAN></B>、经管、政管、外语、继教院、抗干扰<SPAN lang=EN-US>9</SPAN>个单位报送；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>30</SPAN>日：通信、电工、微固、物电、光电、计算机、体育部、电科院、空天院<SPAN lang=EN-US>9</SPAN>个单位报送。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">三、申请材料</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">1</SPAN><SPAN style="FO