(557, 41, '太阳露笑脸，我们青春展现', '', NULL, 0, '<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" align=center><FONT color=#3300ff><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" align=center><FONT color=#3300ff><FONT size=2><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">太阳露笑脸，我们青春展现</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 194.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 18.5"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman"><FONT color=#3300ff size=3>——数学科学学院主办院际篮球友谊赛拉开帷幕</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 194.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 18.5" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman"></SPAN></P></FONT></SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT color=#3300ff><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate IsROCDate="False" IsLunarDate="False" Day="11" Month="10" Year="2010" w:st="on"><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman"></FONT></SPAN></st1:chsdate></FONT></FONT>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5" align=center><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=409" align=baseline border=0></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5">&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5"><FONT size=3><FONT color=#3300ff><st1:chsdate IsROCDate="False" IsLunarDate="False" Day="11" Month="10" Year="2010" w:st="on"><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman"></FONT></SPAN></st1:chsdate></FONT></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5"><FONT color=#3300ff><FONT size=4><st1:chsdate IsROCDate="False" IsLunarDate="False" Day="11" Month="10" Year="2010" w:st="on"><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">2010</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">10</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">11</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">中午</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">12:30</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">，由数学科学学院主办的院际篮球友谊赛在篮球场拉开帷幕。迎着炎炎秋日，学工办钟主任和王老师和数学学院陈主任都莅临现场。数学科学学院、信息学院，外国语学院，政管学院许多同学都前来观战，可以看出这场比赛大家的积极性。参加队员分别来自四个学院的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">8</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">支球队。</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><FONT color=#3300ff><FONT size=4><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">简单热烈开幕式结束以后，学工办的钟主任为队员开球。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">八支球队在两个球场上的球技可谓不相上下，整个过程比分咬得很紧，观众都看得热血沸腾！球员在球场上打的激烈，每个学院的啦啦队也不输了士气，这些啦啦队同学站在太阳下不怕累不怕热给自己学院呐喊助威！新老同学不分专业都凝聚在一起，为自己的学院加油！</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><FONT color=#3300ff><FONT size=4><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT><FONT color=#3300ff><FONT size=4><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">这次的友谊赛是为继教杯篮球赛做准备，虽然只是一场友谊赛，但是各个学院和所有球员都非常认真的对待。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">希望在接下来的比赛中</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">8</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">支球队发挥出更好的水平！也希望数学科学学院把这次友谊联赛办的更加出色，争取到继教杯的主办权！</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>', 1193, 1286930990, '2010-10-12 16:49:50', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(388, 10, '数学学院布置、研讨新学期本科教学工作', '', NULL, 0, '<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 为贯彻学校“走内涵式发展道路，打造一流本科教育”的指导思想，数学科学学院于3月16日召开了本科教学工作会议，黄廷祝院长、高建副院长，各系部主任、书记，数学建模总教练、副总教练及教务科长参加会议。会议围绕学校2010年党政工作要点和本科教育总体目标，进行了相关工作的研讨和布置。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 黄廷祝院长在会上指出，各系部要在过去工作的基础上，在新的一年中进一步解放思想，主要要抓落实，落实人才培养模式和关键教学环节改革方案，推进以研究型教学为核心的教学改革，大力提高本科教学质量和人才培养质量，以改革创新的精神开展各项建设和改革工作，在基础性工作中不断努力，力争在特色专业、精品课程等重点建设项目上有新的突破，取得优异成绩。黄院长还特别强调数学建模教练队，要利用自身所具备的优势，同时也要感到所背负的压力，充分运用优势，选拔人才，重点在培养学生的科技创新能力等。高建副院长对学院近期的教学工作进行了总结和布置，特别强调提高教学质量的关键是要紧紧抓住课堂教学这个基本环节，要求各个系部以不断深入的教学改革为手段，以师资队伍建设为抓手，积极营造研究性课堂教学环境，为实现学校一流本科教育的目标做贡献。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 会上，各系部主任、书记等分别就自己在新的一年中的工作设想也进行了简单的汇报，并针对工作中存在的一些问题进行了热烈地探讨。</P>', 630, 1269398507, '2010-03-23 18:41:47', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(389, 13, '关于开展2010年春季教师资格认定工作的通知', '', NULL, 0, '<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">校内有关单位：</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">接四川省教育厅教师资格认定指导中心《关于开展<SPAN lang=EN-US>2010</SPAN>年春季教师资格认定的通知》（川教资<SPAN lang=EN-US>[2010]01</SPAN>号），现将我校<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">春季教师资格认定</SPAN>工作的有关事宜通知如下：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">一、申请人员</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">我校在职教师。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">二、时间安排</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-highlight: yellow">4</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-highlight: yellow">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>日至<SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>21</SPAN>日</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">：<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">网上报名</SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">申请者登陆中国教师资格网（<U><SPAN lang=EN-US><A href="http://www.jszg.edu.cn/"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">www.jszg.edu.cn</SPAN></A></SPAN></U>），进入教师资格网上申报系统，并根据系统提示填写申请信息，认真核对。确认无误后提交，在线打印<SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN>报名号及现场确认信息<SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN>、《教师资格认定申请表》；下载《申请人思想品德鉴定表》，如实填写并打印。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-highlight: yellow">4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-highlight: yellow">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>22</SPAN>日至<SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>30</SPAN>日</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">：各单位<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">审核申请者材料</SPAN>，并按以下时间统一报人事处师资办公室（沙河校区主楼中<SPAN lang=EN-US>240</SPAN>室，<SPAN lang=EN-US>83202297</SPAN>；清水河校区主楼<SPAN lang=EN-US>B2-502</SPAN>室，<SPAN lang=EN-US>61830536</SPAN>）。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>29</SPAN>日：微固、物电、光电、生命、经管、政管、马克思、外语、体育部、空天院等单位报送；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-highlight: yellow">4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-highlight: yellow">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>30</SPAN>日</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">：通信、电工、计算机、自动化、机电、<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">数学</SPAN>、电科院、抗干扰实验室等单位报送。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">三、<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">申请材料</SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">．《教师资格认定<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">申请表</SPAN>》（<SPAN lang=EN-US style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">A4</SPAN><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">纸</SPAN>）；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">2. </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">《申请人思想品德<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">鉴定表</SPAN>》（<SPAN lang=EN-US>A4</SPAN>纸）；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">．<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">身份证复印件（双面复印）</SPAN>；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">．本人<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">最高学历、最高学位证书复印件</SPAN>；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">5</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">．校医院出具的《四川省教师资格申请人员<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">体格检查表</SPAN>》<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">原</SPAN></B><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">件</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（要求：体检<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">项目齐全</SPAN>，<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">有</SPAN></B>体检<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">结论</SPAN>和体检<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">医院公章</SPAN>）；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">6</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">．《四川省高等学校青年教师职业技能（<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">岗前）培训合格证书</SPAN>》<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: blue; mso-highlight: yellow">或</SPAN></B>《四川<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">省高校教师教育科学理论自学考试合格证》复印件</SPAN>；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">7</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">．<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">普通话</SPAN>水平测试等级（<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">二级乙等以上</SPAN>）证书<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">复印件</SPAN>；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">8</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">．《四川省申请教师资格人员<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">教育教学基本素质和能力审查表</SPAN>》<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">原件</SPAN></B>（申请人根据申请任教学科到所在<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">学科评议组进行测试</SPAN>）；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">9</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">．近期<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">二寸半身正面免冠彩色照片一张</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>(</SPAN>证书使用<SPAN lang=EN-US>)</SPAN>；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">10</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">．教育学硕士免第<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>项；师范教育类专业毕业人员免第<SPAN lang=EN-US>8</SPAN>项，但应提交教育教学实习鉴定表和教育学、教育心理学成绩复印件一份；<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">博士</SPAN><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: blue; mso-highlight: yellow">或</SPAN><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">副教授</SPAN></B>（副研究员）及以上人员<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">免第<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>、<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>、<SPAN lang=EN-US>8</SPAN>项</SPAN>，<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">副教授</SPAN>（副研究员）及以上人员须<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">提供职称证明</SPAN></B>。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">四、注意事项</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">1. </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">申请者网上报名时，认定机构选择</SPAN><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">“</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">四川省教育厅<SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">，工作单位统一填写</SPAN><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">“</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">电子科技大学<SPAN lang=EN-US>”</SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">2. </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">《申请人思想品德<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">鉴定表</SPAN></B>》由学校<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">人事处盖章</SPAN></B>。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">3. </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">申报材料中： <B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">1</SPAN><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">、<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>项</SPAN></B><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">合并装订（</SPAN></SPAN><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-highlight: yellow">一式两份</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-highlight: yellow">）</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">，<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">3</SPAN><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">至<SPAN lang=EN-US>8</SPAN>项</SPAN></B><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">合并装订<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">（一式一份）</B></SPAN>；要求照片的，必须粘贴照片；要求提供复印件的，<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; COLOR: red; mso-highlight: yellow">一律使用<SPAN lang=EN-US>A4</SPAN>纸复印</SPAN></B>，并由所在单位人事干事审核原件、签字并加盖单位公章。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">附件：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">1.<A href="http://www.pd.uestc.edu.cn/content4-1.asp?id=270&amp;gid=6"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US>《四川省申请教师资格人员教育教学基本素质和能力审查表》</SPAN></SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">2.<A href="http://www.pd.uestc.edu.cn/content4-1.asp?id=271&amp;gid=6"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US>《四川省申请认定教师资格人员教育教学<SPAN lang=EN-US>基本素质和能力测试办法（试行）》</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></A></SPAN>', 2046, 1269486629, '2010-03-24 19:10:29', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(390, 19, '2010年暑期腾讯公司招实习通知', '', NULL, 0, '你想体验全球第二大互联网公司吗？你想在全球第二大互联网公司实习吗？你想跟一群技术牛人一起开发吗？<BR>&nbsp;现在腾讯研究院给你提供这样的机会 <BR>&nbsp;腾讯研究院招聘实习生，北京上海深圳都有：<BR>目前急需：<BR>&nbsp; 1. 做过浏览器相关项目的 <BR>&nbsp; 2. 做过手机端软件开发的<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp; 3. windows客户端前台开发<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp; 4. Linux/Unix后台开发<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp; 5. 其他方面的优秀同学同样需要<BR>实习生要求如下：（不限专业，不限学历，只要你符合以下要求（或部分符合））<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.积极向上，有热情<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.技术背景出身，专业能力强，GPA排名位居前<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3.动手能力强，在校期间的项目或课程实践经验丰富<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.ACM、百度之星、数模等大赛的得主或资深参与者<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5.或有在知名IT类公司实习过的经历<BR>时间上的限制：<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一个礼拜至少有4天（工作日），至少要3个月时间，当然越长越好。<BR>&nbsp; 有兴趣的同学可以发送简历到 <A href="mailto:tencentsc@126.com">tencentsc@126.com</A>&nbsp; ，邮件主题注明实习生应聘。<BR>简历请以附件和正文的方式一起发送！谢谢！<BR>腾讯研究院期待您的加入！<BR>其他事项:<BR>1:有同学问实习后留到这里的机会有多大：<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 研究院实习生的招聘基本是按照员工的招聘要求来的，会比较严格。因此，如果实习期间表现良好的话，留下的机会比较大。<BR>2: 来研究院后做什么方向或者项目？<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp; 应该是根据两个方面吧，一是自己的兴趣，另外一个是大家以前项目的背景。<BR>3：关于实习待遇<BR>公司会提供给大家有竞争力的实习待遇和其他补助（包括交通补助、住房补助等）<BR>（PS:腾讯研究院承载公司核心业务线上的多款产品的研发工作。产品涵盖腾讯桌面应用程序，无线/移动应用程序，互联网服务等 <A href="http://research.tencent.com/">http://research.tencent.com/</A>）<BR>', 2240, 1269588648, '2010-03-25 23:30:48', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(391, 11, '学院召开“感悟英雄事迹，发挥党员作用”座谈会', '', NULL, 0, '<P><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=223" align=baseline border=0></P>\r\n<P><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=222" align=baseline border=0></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2010年3月24日，数学科学学院本科08级党支部以“学习英雄事迹，做时代楷模”为主题，组织08、09级所有党员、积极分子在基础教学楼A407召开了感悟英雄事迹，发挥党员作用的座谈会。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 会议中，各位党员介绍了自己的个人经历以及对党的认识，并就自己印象最深刻的一个人物发表了感悟，积极分子也结合自己的入党动机等谈了个人的想法，同时相互间也虚心接受了彼此的意见和建议。其中李凡同学就沈浩英雄事迹的感动之情溢于言表，并多次提议支部再次组织观看“沈浩同志事迹报告会”。其他同学都积极踊跃发言，并不断被彼此的发言感动着，气氛十分活跃。大家深刻体会到了英雄的精神，对我们的思想觉悟产生了很大影响。最后，&nbsp;&nbsp; 会议公布了党支部新吸纳的一批积极分子的名单，党支部书记发言对他们表示祝贺，并对他们提出了严格要求。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 本次活动，让同学们收获颇丰，使中国共产党的位置在同学们心中更加坚定不移，并表示在今后的学习和工作中充分发挥党员的先锋模范带头作用！<BR></P>', 670, 1269589032, '2010-03-25 23:37:12', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(392, 17, '关于评选大学生综合A级证书的通知', '', NULL, 0, '<P><FONT size=3>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 现已展开2010年大学生“综合素质A级证书”的评选工作，现将共青团四川省委关于开展2010年大学生“综合素质A级证书”评选的通知发出，请大家4月9号之前将申报表交到学院办公室（主楼A1区516房间），电子档发到</FONT><A href="mailto:yepy2007@126.com"><FONT size=3>yepy2007@126.com</FONT></A></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=3>附件：关于开展2010年大学生“综合素质A级证书”评选的通知</FONT></P>', 1635, 1269590457, '2010-03-26 00:00:57', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
