> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">人</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">樊卫国</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">副教授</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告地点</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">： 清水河校区主楼<SPAN lang=EN-US>A1-512<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告时间：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">6</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>23</SPAN>日（周三）上午<SPAN lang=EN-US>9</SPAN>：<SPAN lang=EN-US>30<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告人简介：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体"> </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">樊卫国副教授</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">1995</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年本科毕业于西安交通大学，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">1998</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年在新加坡国立大学取得硕士学位，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">2002</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年在美国密歇根大学取得博士学位，现为美国弗吉尼亚理工大学会计与信息系统系副教授，主要研究方向为商业智能、文本挖掘、信息检索、知识管理、信息一体化等。先后在《</SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">IEEE Tra</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt">nsactions on Knowledge and Data </SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">Engineering</SPAN></FONT><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">》、《</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">ACM Transactions on Internet Technology</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">》等国际著名学术期刊或学术会议上发表论文近百篇，担任</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">《</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">Journal of Database Management</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">》</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Wingdings; mso-hansi-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings">和</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Wingdings; mso-hansi-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">《</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">Journal of Electronic Commerce Research and Applications</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">》</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">两个杂志的编委，担任</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Wingdings; mso-hansi-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">《</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">Journal of Electronic Commerce Research</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-