IZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">人</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman">：</SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体"> <SPAN lang=EN-US>Prof. </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt">Zhuangyi Liu<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告地点</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">： </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman">清水河校区主楼</SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt">A1-503</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">报告时间：</SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"> </SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">10</SPAN></FONT><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">25</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">日（周一）上午</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">9</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">：</SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">30</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=Default style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">报告人简介：</SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">刘壮一教授本科毕业于复旦大学，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">1989</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">年在美国弗吉利亚理工大学获得博士学位，现任美国明尼苏达大学杜卢斯分校数学系系主任。刘教授的主要研究领域是最优控制、参数识别、数值逼近等，目前担任国际刊物《</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">Journal of Mathematical Science, Advances and Applications</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">》的主编，至今已发表学术论文五十余篇。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-FAMILY: 新宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><o:p><FONT size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 120%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 120%; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 110%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-layout-grid-align: none" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 110%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; LINE-HEIGHT: 110%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-layout-grid-align: none" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 110%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">欢迎全校师生参加！<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>', 1234, 1287631098, '2010-10-20 19:18:18', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
