mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">研</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">究</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">兴</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">趣</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">为</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">非</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">线</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">性方程<SPAN lang=EN-US>(</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">组</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">)</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">的近似求解算法以及</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">数值优</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">化中</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">与</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">之相</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">关</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">的算法的</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">构</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">造及分析</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">研</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">究。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">发</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">表的<SPAN lang=EN-US>SCI</SPAN>收</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">录论</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">文中，<SPAN lang=EN-US>SCI</SPAN>他引<SPAN lang=EN-US>50</SPAN>余</SPAN> ', 926, 1290499763, '2010-11-23 00:09:23', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(594, 12, '数学学院学术报告-南开大学王永进教授', '', NULL, 0, '<P class=NoSpacing style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 26pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman">学术报告</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 26pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=NoSpacing style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=NoSpacing style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">报告题目：</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">从现代概率论到金融信用风险</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=NoSpacing style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">报 告 人：</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">南开大学王永进教授</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=NoSpacing style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">报告时间：</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">2010</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">年<SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>日上午<SPAN lang=EN-US>9:10</SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=NoSpacing style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体"><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">报告地点：</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">清水河校区主楼<SPAN lang=EN-US>A1</SPAN>区<SPAN lang=EN-US>512</SPAN>室</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=NoSpacing style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">报告人介绍：</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=NoSpacing style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">王永进，南开大学数学科学学院、商学院教授、博士生导师。<SPAN lang=EN-US>1986</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>月本科毕业于国防科技大学应用数学系；<SPAN lang=EN-US>1992</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>月博士研究生毕业于南开大学数学系概率统计专业（导师<SPAN lang=EN-US>: </SPAN>王梓坤院士）。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=NoSpacing style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">学术研究领域：概率论与随机过程；金融风险定价。<SPAN lang=EN-US> <o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=NoSpacing style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">目前正主持教育部重大项目</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">金融信用风险的量化研究</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">（<SPAN lang=EN-US>2009,<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>01—2011, 12</SPAN>）， 和主持国家自然科学基金（数理部）项目：超过程与相关<SPAN lang=EN-US>SPDE</SPAN>的研究（<SPAN lang=EN-US>2009, 01---2011, 12</SPAN>）。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=NoSpacing style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">王永进教授曾先后应邀前往进行学术合作的国际机构和大学包括<SPAN lang=EN-US>: </SPAN>德国柏林维尔斯特拉斯<SPAN lang=EN-US>(Weierstrass</SPAN>）应用分析与随机研究所；加拿大菲尔兹<SPAN lang=EN-US>(Fields)</SPAN>数学研究所、太平洋数学研究所、不列颠哥伦比亚大学、卡尔顿大学；澳大利亚墨尔本大学；英国牛津大学和曼彻斯特大学、伦敦政治经济学院等。并先后在世界二十多个大学和研究机构作学术报告。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=NoSpacing style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">王永进教授在南开大学数学科学学院长期主讲本科生基础课</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">概率论</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">；本科高年级和研究生专业课</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">随机过程</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">。并讲授</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">应用随机过程</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">金融信用风险</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">等应用领域的专业课程。<SPAN lang=EN-US> <o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=NoSpacing style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">王永进曾担任南开大学数学科学学院院长（<SPAN lang=EN-US>2003--2008</SPAN>）等行政职务，现任南开大学商学院副院长；并曾任中国概率统计学会常务理事（<SPAN lang=EN-US>2002—2006</SPAN>），现任中国金融工程学会常务理事（<SPAN lang=EN-US>2008—2012</SPAN>）。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', 1687, 1290499806, '2010-11-23 00:10:06', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(595, 12, '六位青年教师获批国家自然科学基金项目立项', '', NULL, 0, '<H2 style="MARGIN: auto 0cm; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style="mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">六位青年教师获批国家自然科学基金项目立项</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></H2>\r\n<P class=a style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=a style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">据悉，今年我院六位青年教师获批国家自然科学基金项目立项，分别是：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=a style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=a style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">欧耀彬副教授获批<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">国家自然科学基金青年基金项目</B>立项。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=a style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=a style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">雷银彬、原子霞、程光辉、李厚彪、李良五位青年教师分别获批<B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">国家自然科学基金数学天元青年基金项目</B>立项。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', 1344, 1290575767, '2010-11-23 21:16:07', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(596, 41, '电子科技大学“成电纵横”职业篮球培训赛拉开帷幕', '', NULL, 0, '<SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=center><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">电子科技大学“成电纵横”篮球赛拉开帷幕</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 15.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5" align=left><FONT size=3><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate w:st="on" IsROCDate="False" IsLunarDate="False" Day="22" Month="11" Year="2010"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">11</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">22</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">下午</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">4</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">点，一年一度的电子科技大学</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">“</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">成电纵横</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">”</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">篮球赛在沙河校区篮球场开赛了！</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp; &nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">到场的嘉宾有王军副院长、钟主任等多位领导，在白忙之中抽出时间亲临现场。参加我们的开幕式！在开幕式上首先由王军副院长向各位球员致辞！学校领导希望在本届篮球赛中，球员们发扬友谊第一，比赛第二的精神，团结互助，在比赛中进步，赛出风格、赛出水平、赛出品格；同时希望裁判员们坚守岗位，公平公正，尽职尽责。最后他预祝本届篮球赛圆满成功！运动员代表、裁判员代表分别发表讲话表示不负领导和老师们的期望，在本届球赛中努力拼搏，团结协作，为比赛的圆满成功尽自己的最大努力！</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">联赛由电子科技大学数学科学学院和计算机与工程学院联合主办，共有</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">19</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">个学院参加比赛，本届篮球赛将从</SPAN><st1:chsdate w:st="on" IsROCDate="False" IsLunarDate="False" Day="22" Month="11" Year="2010"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">11</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 170%; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-fami