(625, 11, '2011年寒假学生安全须知', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">关于寒假期间安全注意事项的通知<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体><FONT size=3>根据学校通知，今年学生寒假时间为<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>17</SPAN>日（周一）～<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>18</SPAN>日（周五）。下学期学生注册时间为<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>19</SPAN>、<SPAN lang=EN-US>20</SPAN>日，<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>21</SPAN>日正式上课。为了让广大同学度过一个愉快、平安的假期，特提醒注意以下事项：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial , sans-serif; COLOR: black; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face=宋体>一、遵守国家法律法规和校规校纪，遵守社会公德，做文明公民。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体>二、服从学校教学安排，不提前离校，不逾期返校，按时注册。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体>三、宿舍内不留宿他人，注意宿舍防盗、防火，杜绝使用明火、违章电器，外出要关窗、反锁门并关闭电源。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体>四、同学离校前，请在辅导员和楼栋管理员处登记。今年寒假继续实行集中住宿，晚离校和不离校本科生请在辅导员处登记，并和学院留校学生负责人保持联系，离校时请在楼栋管理员处登记。外出时间较长或外出活动人数较多时，应提前告知学院留校学生负责人，留下联系方式。学生提前返校到楼栋管理员处办理登记手续。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体>五、树立安全意识。寒假期间要注意饮食卫生和人身、财产安全。建议不要单独外出旅游，不与不熟悉的人员外出旅游，不到人员过于拥挤或未开发的区域游玩，不要乘坐无证、无照人员驾驶的车、船等交通工具，外出游玩时特别注意冰上安全、水上安全和交通安全。外出时间较长或人数较多时，请提前告知家长或学校。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体>六、春节时，同学应当在法律许可的时间、地点安全燃放烟花爆竹，避免对集体和个人人身、财产安全造成危害。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体>七、除注意自身安全外，要注意防范身边出现的安全隐患和不稳定因素，发现可疑情况及时向有关部门报告。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体>八、学院应树立责任意识，面向学生依法开展安全、文明燃放烟花爆竹的宣传、教育活动，并开展交通安全、饮食卫生、防火、防盗、防骗、防中毒、防溺水等方面的提醒和教育工作。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体>九、学校值班电话<SPAN lang=EN-US>:<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 23.95pt; mso-para-margin-left: 2.28gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体>学 生 处：（清水河校区）<SPAN lang=EN-US>61830078</SPAN>，(沙河校区）<SPAN lang=EN-US>83201997<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 23.95pt; mso-para-margin-left: 2.28gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体>研 工 部：<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>83200018<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 23.95pt; mso-para-margin-left: 2.28gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></SPAN>校 园<SPAN lang=EN-US>110</SPAN>：（清水河校区）<SPAN lang=EN-US>61830110</SPAN>，（沙河校区）<SPAN lang=EN-US>83200110<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体>预祝各位同学寒假愉快，春节快乐！<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; TEXT-INDENT: 384pt; mso-char-indent-count: 32.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体>学生处<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; TEXT-INDENT: 384pt; mso-char-indent-count: 32.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体>研究生工作部<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">保卫处<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; TEXT-INDENT: 384pt; mso-char-indent-count: 32.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial" lang=EN-US>2010</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">年<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>日<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>', 924, 1294899272, '2011-01-12 22:14:32', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
