(627, 22, '关于我校留学研究生课程面向部分硕士研究生开放的通知', '', NULL, 0, '<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">关于我校留学研究生课程面向部分硕士研究生开放的通知</SPAN></P><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman "></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">硕士研究生同学：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 22pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">为促进我校全日制研究生与留学研究生之间相互交流与学习，搭建良好的国际生学术交流平台，经研究决定，留学研究生专业课程面向我校部分硕士研究生开放。具体规定如下：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">一、申请对象：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">我校全日制硕士研究生，且专业与留学研究生所开课程相关或相近；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">英语水平较好，即在入学时参与英语分级考试、定为</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">A</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">级；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">学有余力。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">二、申请登记及选拔方式：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">达到申请要求的研究生，随堂填写选课登记表，向任课教师申请。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">任课教师负责遴选、考核申请者的英语水平与专业水平，确定并公布入选的硕士研究生选课名单。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">三、选课及学分认定：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">留学研究生的专业课程（含专业基础课、专业课）均为全英文教学，全日制研究生所选全部作为选修课，通过者获取相应学分。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">选修留学研究生课程不受学分限制。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">四、成绩说明：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">全日制研究生所选留学生课程所获成绩，将统一并入学生个人成绩单。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">五、其他：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">我校留学研究生正式开课时间：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">21</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">日。选课截止时间：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">6</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">日。具体课表详见附件。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman "></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">研究生院</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate w:st="on" Year="2011" Month="2" Day="21" IsLunarDate="False" IsROCDate="False"><FONT face="Times New Roman">2011</FONT><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman "><SPAN lang=EN-US>年</SPAN></SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman">2</FONT><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman "><SPAN lang=EN-US>月</SPAN></SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman">21</FONT><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman "><SPAN lang=EN-US>日</SPAN></SPAN></st1:chsdate><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center></o:p></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>', 878, 1298444347, '2011-02-22 22:59:07', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(628, 10, '本学期《微积分》课程答疑安排', '', NULL, 0, '详见附件，并请严格按照附件表中时间、地点执行。', 611, 1298597690, '2011-02-24 17:34:50', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(629, 20, '早稻田大学信息生产系统研究生院留学项目推介会通知', '', NULL, 0, '<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早稻田大学（WASEDA University），它是日本最负盛名的大学之一。100多年以来，早稻田大学为日本培养了众多的政界、经济界和文化界的著名人士，如福田康夫、田中真纪子、小渊惠三、松下幸之助、北原白秋、坪内逍遥等。另外，许多中国现代人物，如李大钊、彭湃、廖承志等，都曾在早大留学。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早稻田大学大学院信息生产系统研究生院（位于日本福冈县北九州市，简称IPS）同意接收我校推荐的优秀本科毕业生赴早稻田大学大学院攻读硕士学位，学时二年，（4＋2项目）；同时，早稻田大学也接收我校一年级在读研究生赴该校学习，考核合格可授予早稻田大学硕士学位，返校后符合我校的相关规定，亦可授予我校硕士学位，（1＋1项目）。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早稻田大学大学院信息生产系统研究生院院长平泽宏太郎先生将来我校举行留学项目推介会，届时将会对提交申请材料的学生进行现场面试，欢迎我校有意赴日本留学的同学积极参会并进行现场咨询。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 宣讲会时间：3月2日（周三）10:30AM<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 地点：清水河校区科C-216<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 申请材料领取地点：清水河校区主楼B3-204<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 联系电话：61830602<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 电子科技大学国际合作与交流处<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2011年2月25日&nbsp; </P>', 1264, 1298609783, '2011-02-24 20:56:23', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `article` (`articleid`, `sortid`, `title`, `source`, `author`, `userid`, `content`, `click`, `publish_time`, `launch_time`, `imageid`, `keyword1`, `keyword2`, `keyword3`) VALUES
(630, 12, '关于提交自然基金申请的通知', '', NULL, 0, '<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 根据科技处的时间安排，请各位老师务必于3月9日下午4：00之前交两份申请书纸质版（请本人签字）、会签表纸质版一份，申请书电子版一份传到我邮箱（不接受U盘拷贝）。</P>\r\n<P>关于申请书的注意事项：<BR>1、提交的申请书纸版和电子版务必保证版本号一致；<BR>2、会签表财务处签字一栏请自己到清水河财务处B3-305于超老师处签字，B2-304王萍副处长签字，B2-303盖章；<BR>3、如果申请书涉及到外单位人员，申请书最后一页请务必到对方单位盖章（如果是学校，需盖对方学校校章），如项目组成员是国外机构人员，请务必提供该成员亲笔签名的同意书（最好是原件，如果时间来不及可为传真件或扫描打印件）。<BR></P>', 923, 1298860445, '2011-02-27 18:34:05', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(631, 22, '南阳师范学院招聘启事', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">南阳师范学院坐落在南阳市卧龙岗上，具有百年办学历史，是河南省属全日制普通本科高等院校。南阳物华天宝，人杰地灵，山川秀美，交通便利，享有绿城、水城、历史文化名城、现代化新城之美誉；南阳文化积淀悠久而丰厚，曾孕育了张衡、张仲景、诸葛亮、范蠡等历史名人，近现代更是有冯友兰、姚雪垠、彭雪枫、王永民、二月河等英才涌现。学校占地<SPAN lang=EN-US>1857</SPAN>亩，现有教职工<SPAN lang=EN-US>1314</SPAN>人，其中具有博士、硕士学位教师<SPAN lang=EN-US>635</SPAN>人，教授、副教授等高级专业技术人员<SPAN lang=EN-US>385</SPAN>人，设有<SPAN lang=EN-US>20</SPAN>个学院<SPAN lang=EN-US>54</SPAN>个本科专业，涵盖了文、史、理、工、法、教育、经济、管理、农学等<SPAN lang=EN-US>9</SPAN>个学科门类。为适应发展需要，特向全国诚聘优秀人才。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">一、拟招聘人员的基本条件<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（一）具有中华人民共和国国籍；<SPAN lang=EN-US> <o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（二）坚持四项基本原则，热爱教育事业，思想进步，作风正派，遵纪守法；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（三）身心健康，能胜任教学、科研工作；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（四）博士后出站人员、全日制普通高校应届博士毕业生或到<SPAN lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>月前尚在择业期内未就业的全日制博士毕业生，<SPAN lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>月底年龄不超过<SPAN lang=EN-US>35</SPAN>周岁；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（五）全日制普通高校应届硕士研究生毕业生或到<SPAN lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>月前尚在择业期内未就业的全日制硕士研究生：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">①<SPAN lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>月底年龄不超过<SPAN lang=EN-US>30</SPAN>周岁；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">②具有全日制普通本科学历；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">③全日制硕士研究生阶段原则上在<SPAN lang=EN-US>211</SPAN>院校就读。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（六）本科阶段所学专业、研究生阶段所学专业与所招聘的专业相同或相近。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（七）国外取得硕士学位人员的学位、学历须取得国家教育部留学服务中心的认证。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（八）艺术类、紧缺专业的条件根据专业需要适当放宽。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">二</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">、拟招聘专业、人数<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">详见《南阳师范学院<SPAN lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN>年度招聘教师计划》<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">三、受聘待遇<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（一）两院院士、国家级“百千万人才工程”第一层人选、教育部“长江学者奖励计划”特聘教授、省级特聘教授、省级学术技术带头人（正高职）和在本领域本专业有独特造诣的专家，学校将提供优厚待遇，具体面议。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（二）引进到我校工作的博士后、博士研究生（指学位、学历俱全的全日制毕业生），完成规定的教学、科研和其它工作任务，在服务期内（<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>年），根据专业不同享受不同待遇，具体待遇如下：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">、紧缺专业：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>）学校帮助联系房源，并发给安家费<SPAN lang=EN-US>25</SPAN>万元；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>）享受档案工资和校内岗位津贴；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>）科研启动费文科及非实验性理科<SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>～<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>万元，实验性理科<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>～<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>万元；凡省部级以上资助项目，学校按资助金额给予<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>：<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>配套。对于科研水平特别突出的，科研启动费可在原科研启动费的基础上增加<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>～<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>万元。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（<SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>）帮助解决子女入学（小学、初中）问题。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>）配偶为硕士研究生的可随调。安排配偶工作后，引进博士的安家费为<SPAN lang=EN-US>17</SPAN>万元。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">、非紧缺专业<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>）学校帮助联系房源，并发给安家费<SPAN lang=EN-US>15</SPAN>万元；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>）享受档案工资和校内岗位津贴；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>）科研启动费文科及非实验性理科<SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>～<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>万元，实验性理科<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>～<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>万元；凡省部级以上资助项目，学校按资助金额给予<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>：<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>配套。对于科研水平特别突出的，科研启动费可在原科研启动费的基础上增加<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>～<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>万元。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（<SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>）帮助解决子女入学（小学、初中）问题。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>）配偶为硕士研究生的根据工作需要可随调。安排配偶工作后，引进博士的安家费为<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>万元。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（三）招聘到我校的硕士研究生实行人事代理。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（四）引进人员须与学校签订服务年限及违约责任的《协议书》方能享受上述待遇。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">四、招聘程序及方法</SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（一）报名<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">应聘者可通过邮寄、发送电子邮件等方式将个人简历发送到南阳师院人事处，电子邮箱：<SPAN lang=EN-US>nysyrsc</SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">＠</B><SPAN lang=EN-US>126.com</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black">。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 29.55pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.46" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">温馨提示：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 29.55pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.46" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">、由于应聘简历较多，请投送电子简历的应聘者务必在邮件主题和附件标题加注“姓名<SPAN lang=EN-US>+</SPAN>专业<SPAN lang=EN-US>+</SPAN>学历<SPAN lang=EN-US>+</SPAN>应聘岗位”等信息，如：“王名<SPAN lang=EN-US>+</SPAN>企业管理<SPAN lang=EN-US>+</SPAN>博士<SPAN lang=EN-US>+</SPAN>应聘企业管理教师”。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">、根据教育厅统一安排，应聘人员必须在“河南省属大中专学校教师招聘管理系统”报名后方有资格进入下一轮程序，请及时关注教育厅网站公布的该系统开通时间及报名相关事宜，以免错过报名时间。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（二）资格审查<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">人事处对照招聘条件、招聘专业对应聘材料进行初审；通过初审人员的简历转发到相关院（室），各院（室）根据需要，按照招聘人数和试讲人数不低于<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>：<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>的比例拟定试讲人员。拟定的试讲人员到校试讲时，须携带相关材料先到人事处进行资格审查。对应聘人员的资格审查将贯穿招聘工作的全过程，应聘人员提供的材料及填报的信息如有不实情况，一经发现，随时取消应聘资格。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">拟定试讲人员须携带材料如下：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">、毕业生就业推荐表，就业协议书（最好是毕业院校已经盖章）；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: list 74.0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">、各类获奖证书原件及复印件；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: list 74.0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">、各类等级证书（外语、计算机、普通话等）原件及复印件；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: list 74.0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">、身份证原件及复印件；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: list 74.0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>5</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">、本科毕业证书、学位证书原件及复印件，研究生毕业证书、学位证书原件及复印件；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: list 74.0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>6</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">、本科、研究生学习阶段的成绩单及复印件；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: list 74.0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>7</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">、近期免冠<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>寸照片<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>张；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; tab-stops: list 74.0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>8</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">、如果发表有论文，须提供论文原件，在网上可以查到的论文可只提供论文题目；完成有科研项目的，提供结项证书或鉴定证书原件。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（三）考试内容和方法<SPAN lang=EN-US> <o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">应聘人员的考试分为笔试、试讲和面试。笔试、试讲、面试分别按百分制打分，最后按笔试成绩占<SPAN lang=EN-US>30%</SPAN>，试讲成绩占<SPAN lang=EN-US>50</SPAN>％，面试成绩占<SPAN lang=EN-US>20</SPAN>％的比例折合应聘人员的考试总成绩。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">五、联系方式<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">通讯地址：河南省南阳市卧龙路<SPAN lang=EN-US>1638</SPAN>号　<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">南阳师范学院人事处　<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN>邮 编：<SPAN lang=EN-US>473061<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">联系人：<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN>王老师<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN>刘老师<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN>杨老师<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">联系电话：<SPAN lang=EN-US>0377</SPAN>－<SPAN lang=EN-US>63513710<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体>传真：<SPAN lang=EN-US>0377</SPAN>－<SPAN lang=EN-US>63513710<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black"><FONT size=3><FONT face=宋体>邮箱：<SPAN lang=EN-US><A href="mailto:nysyrsc@126.com"><FONT color=#0000ff>nysyrsc@126.com</FONT></A><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; LINE-HEIGHT: 25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=宋体>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>', 1031, 1299143382, '2011-03-03 01:09:42', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(632, 10, '2007级毕业设计初期检查安排表', '', NULL, 0, '2007级毕业设计初期检查安排表', 939, 1299220891, '2011-03-03 22:41:31', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(633, 11, '数学科学学院开展2011年学生工作布置会', '', NULL, 0, '<P align=center><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=507"></P>\r\n<P align=center><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=508"></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">日下午</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>16:20</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">，数学科学学院针对本学院学生干部开展了</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">年学生工作布置会，参会对象包括了学生会、分团委、党支部、班级和研分会等所有学院学生干部，由学院党委苟生平副书记做总体的工作布置。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">此次学生工作布置会是基于学院学生工作队伍对四年规划及</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">年学生工作的理解和讨论下进行的。苟书记以学风建设为主线，解读了构建适应创新人才培养的三支队伍、三项机制和三大举措的“三位一体”高校学生工作体系，通过对组织、管理、工作三大体系的认真执行顺利并高效的完成四年规划，并且详细的介绍了本年度学生工作的重点，为干部后期工作的开展指明了方向。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">最后，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>07</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>08</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">级辅导员叶谱英老师针对本学期优秀党支部创建、毕业生文化活动及日常管理工作进行布置并提出了要求。</SPAN></FONT><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>', 942, 1299226525, '2011-03-04 00:15:25', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(634, 19, '行健 致远——华为公司专场座谈会', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">新学期伊始，应届毕业生的就业工作进入新的阶段。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">日下午，华为公司人力资源专员来到我院与本硕应届毕业生进行交流，通过详实的数据展示了华为公司今年的发展态势及行业内优势，丰富的图片和视频资料展现了华为公司国际化的工作、生活环境，表达了华为公司在专业人才需求及培养方面的诚挚意愿。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><FONT size=3>谈到本次座谈，人力资源老师表示，华为公司随着业务的拓展及深入，越来越清晰地认识到数学专业人才在职业发展道路上的无穷潜力。无论是思维能力还是专业核心领域的研究学习能力，数学人都表现出明显优势，这也是他们在人才需求上做出调整的原因。吸纳更多国内一流大学数学专业人才进入华为，是他们接下来的计划。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><FONT size=3>作为数学学科的学生，要认识到专业发展潜力，打牢基础，广泛涉猎相关应用方向的知识，为今后的职业成长做好铺垫。</FONT></SPAN></P>', 1305, 1299228989, '2011-03-04 00:56:29', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
