s New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告地点</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">： 清水河校区主楼<SPAN lang=EN-US>A1-512<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告时间：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> </FONT></SPAN><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate w:st="on" IsROCDate="False" IsLunarDate="False" Day="10" Month="3" Year="2011"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">（周四）上午<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>：<SPAN lang=EN-US>30<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告人简介：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">高木英明博士于</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">1969 </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年至</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">1974 </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年在东京大学理学部物理学科，获得学士和硕士学位。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">1974 </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">—1993 </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年在</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">IBM</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">工作，任东京基础研究所基础理论部次长。其间获得</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">IBM</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">海外学者奖学金于</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">1979</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">—1983</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">在</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">University of California Los Angeles</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">（</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">UCLA</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">），进入雷纳德</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">·</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">克兰罗克（</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">Leonard Kleinrock</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">，被称为因特网之父）的实验室学习，获得计算机科学博士，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">1993</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年至现在</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">, </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">任日本筑波大学经营政策科学学院院长，系统信息科学学院专攻长，教授。其间曾担任筑波大学主管科研的副校长。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">高木英明博士是日本排队论及其在通信网络应用研究领域的代表人物。他出版了五本引用率很高的排队论，通信系统性能评价方面的专著：</SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-style: italic" lang=EN-US>Analysis of Polling Systems</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US> (The MIT Press, 1986), <SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-style: italic">Queueing Analysis</SPAN></SPAN></FONT><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-style: italic">，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman"> Volumes 1-3 (Elsevier, 1991-1993)</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">，</SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman"> <SPAN lang=EN-US>Spectrum Requirement Planning in Wireless Communications</SPAN></FONT><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">John Wiley and Sons, 2008.</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">）。因为在通信网络的排队模型方向的贡献，他于</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">1996</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年当选</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">IEEE Fellow</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">2001</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=JA>年获</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">IFIP Silver Core</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=JA>，</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">2009</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=JA>年获得通信技术奖（电气通信普及财团）。高木英明博士还担任了包括</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-style: italic; mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">IEEE Transactions on Communications</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-style: italic; mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=JA>，</SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-style: italic; mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=EN-US>IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=EN-US> </SPAN></FONT><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=JA>，</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-style: italic; mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">Performance Evaluation</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-style: italic; mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=JA>，</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-style: italic; mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">Queueing Systems</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-style: italic; mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=JA>等杂志</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-fareast-language: JA" lang=JA>的编辑。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 15.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">高木英明博士还是</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">筑波学园都市<SPAN lang=EN-US>NPO</SPAN>组织<SPAN lang=EN-US>Tsumugi Tsukuba</SPAN>的法人代表，组织的主旨是促进作为日本的科研院所集中区的筑波市的科研成果向产业方面的转化<SPAN lang=EN-US>.</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告摘要：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman">Telephone call centers are an integral part of many businesses, and their economic role is significant and growing. They are also fascinating socio-technical systems in which the behavior of customers and employees is closely intertwined with physical performance measures. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US>We begin with a tutorial on how call centers function and proceed to survey academic research devoted to the management of their operations. We then review the state of research on queueing models for telephone call centers. Finally, we give an </SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>exposition of theoretical results for the M/M/m queueing system with </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US>impatient customer as a widely used model of call centers.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 110%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 110%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt">欢迎全校师生参加！<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>', 938, 1299476335, '2011-03-06 21:38:55', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(636, 10, '数学学院、物电学院研讨“数理基科班”培养模式', '', NULL, 0, '<P><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=510"></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman">按照汪校长在学校</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman">年党政工作研讨会上关于</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">数理基础科学班</SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US> </SPAN></FONT><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman">人才培养模式改革<SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">的讲话精神，</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">数学学院和物电学院积极开展了关于“数理基科班”人才培养模式改革的研究，并就目前的研究情况和思路向校领导和教务处领导进行了汇报。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate Year="2011" Month="3" Day="8" IsLunarDate="False" IsROCDate="False"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">月</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">8</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">上午，</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman">数学学院</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">和</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman">物电学院两个学院的院领导和骨干教师代表在数学学院召开了第一次研讨会，校长助理、教务处杨亚培处长和蒋宁副处长应邀参会指导。研讨会就我校</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">“基科班”的</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">目标定位、</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman">培养模式、培养过程、</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">招生与规模、政策保障、管理机制等诸多问题进行了广泛研讨。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman">此前，数学学院在全院大会上传达学习了学校党政工作研讨会<SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">精神，</SPAN>成立了<SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">研究小组并赴清华大学深入学习其</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">“数理基科班”办学</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">成功经验。</SPAN></P>', 782, 1299634779, '2011-03-08 17:39:39', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(637, 22, '关于2010-2011-2前10周研究生课程补选的通知', '', NULL, 0, '<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-alt: 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">2010-2011-2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">前</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">10</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">周网上选课已经结束，针对部分研究生错过规定的选课时间，网上选课未能成功，</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-alt: 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">为保证尽可能的顺利选修研究生相关课程，现将补选办法通知如下：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-alt: 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">1.</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">下载附件《电子科技大学研究生课程补选申请表》并打印填写相关信息。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-alt: 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">2.</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">补选申请单提交给补选课程的任课教师，经任课教师同意并签字后，交任课教师所在学院研究生科，</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-alt: 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">经教学秘书同意后签字并盖章。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-alt: 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">3.</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">将填好的补选申请单交至研究生院教学管理科（主楼中</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">B3-106</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">）。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-alt: 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">4.</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">对于错过选课时间的同学处理方法同上（每门课程均需要提交补选申请单）。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-alt: 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">5.</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">补选申请单受理时间为</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">9</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">日</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">——3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">15</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">日，超过规定时间的补选申请概不受理。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-alt: 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><U><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 备注：网上选课截止后，所有课程类别和考核方式均不能修改。补选课程只能补选人数未达到上限人数的课程（</SPAN></U><U><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">/</FONT></SPAN></U><U><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">班），</SPAN></U></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-alt: 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><U><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">教学管理科不再受理对已满课程</SPAN></U><U><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">(/</FONT></SPAN></U><U><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">班</SPAN></U><U><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">)</FONT></SPAN></U><U><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">的补选</SPAN></U><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-line-height-alt: 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">特此通知</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=3>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">研究生院教学管理科</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;"><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;"><FONT face="Times New Roman">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;"><FONT face="Times New Roman">9</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">日</SPAN></P>', 790, 1299723113, '2011-03-09 18:11:53', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(638, 9, '关于2011年“挑战杯”大学生课外科技作品竞赛校内选拔赛的通知', '', NULL, 0, '<P>各学院、相关单位：&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp; “挑战杯”全国大学生课外学术科技作品竞赛是由共青团中央、中国科协、教育部、全国学联主办的大学生课外学术科技活动中一项具有导向性、示范性和群众性的竞赛活动，第十二届“挑战杯 ”全国大学生课外学术科技作品竞赛将于 2011 年下半年举行 。为迎接第十二届“挑战杯”全国大学生课外学术科技作品竞赛，选拔优秀作品参赛，引导和激励我校大学生刻苦钻研、勇于创新，活跃校园学术气氛，培养学生崇尚科学、团结协作、敢于挑战的科学精神，提高学生的科技创新和实践动手能力，促进学生全面成长成才，展示我校学生课外科技创新水平，积极备战2011年“挑战杯”四川省及全国大学生课外科技作品竞赛，我校将举办2011年“挑战杯”大学生课外科技作品竞赛校内选拔赛。现将有关事宜通知如下，请认真遵照执行：</P>\r\n<P>一、比赛背景</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp; “挑战杯”全国大学生课外学术科技作品竞赛（以下简称“挑战杯”）是由共青团中央、中国科协、教育部、全国学联主办的一项具有导向性、示范性和群众性的全国竞赛活动，被誉为中国大学生学术科技的“奥林匹克”，每两年举办一届。自1989年第一届“挑战杯”举办以来，“挑战杯”竞赛规模发展到包括港、澳、台地区在内的全国1000多所高校，高校参与面达70%以上，已成为全国大学生课外学术科技领域中层次最高、规模最大、参赛范围最广的群众性赛事，是当代大学生展现课外学术科技成果和综合素质的重要舞台，是国内各个大学展示教学科研能力和综合实力的重要窗口。 </P>\r\n<P>二、参赛对象</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp; 全日制非成人教育的中国籍专科生、本科生、硕士研究生和博士研究生（均不含在职研究生）都可申报作品参赛。<BR>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>三、报名要求</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp; 比赛的作品必须是2009年9月1日后完成的且已经完成的学生课外学术科技或社会实践活动成果，可分为个人作品和集体作品。申报个人作品的，申报者必须承担申报作品60％以上的研究工作，作品鉴定证书、专利证书及发表的有关作品上的署名均应为第一作者，合作者必须是学生且不得超过两人；凡作者超过三人的项目或者不超过三人，但无法区分第一作者的项目，均须申报集体作品。集体作者必须均为学生。凡有合作者的个人作品或集体作品，均按学历最高的作者划分至本专科生、硕士研究生或博士研究生类进行评审。参赛作品须经本人或集体报名，有至少一名具有高级专业技术职称的指导老师（或教研组）推荐。毕业设计和课程设计（论文）、学年论文和学位论文、国际竞赛上获奖的作品、获国家级奖励成果（含本竞赛主办单位参与举办的其它全国性竞赛的获奖作品）等不在申报范围之列。 </P>\r\n<P>四、作品类别</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp; 申报参赛的作品须从实际出发，侧重解决社会生产生活中的具体问题。申报类别分为以下三类：</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp; 1、自然科学类学术论文。</P>\r\n<P>作品分类如下：</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp; A.机械与控制（包括机械、仪器仪表、自动化控制、工程、交通、建筑等）；</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp; B.信息技术（包括计算机、电信、通讯、电子等）；</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp; C.数理（包括数学、物理、地球与空间科学等）；</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp; D.生命科学（包括生物、农学、药学、医学、健康、卫生、食品等）；</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp; E.能源化工（包括能源、材料、石油、化学、化工、生态、环保等）。</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp; 2、哲学社会科学类社会调查报告和学术论文。</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp; 作品所属领域限定在哲学、经济、社会、法律、教育、管理六个学科内。</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp; 3、科技发明制作类。</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp; 科技发明制作类分为A、B两类：</P>\r\n<P>A类指科技含量较高、制作投入较大的作品；</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; B类指投入较少，且为生产技术或社会生活带来便利的小发明、小制作等。</P>\r\n<P>作品分类同自然科学类学术论文A—E类。 </P>\r\n<P>五、竞赛日程与安排</P>\r\n<P>1.各学院组织作品及预审阶段（3月1日——4月10日）</P>\r\n<P>（1）3月1日，组委会办公室下发《关于举行电子科技大学2011年“挑战杯”大学生课外学术科技作品竞赛的通知》的文件。《作品申报书》、《参赛作品汇总表》及相关参考资料请在创新创业中心网站（<A href="http://www.incubator.uestc.edu.cn">www.incubator.uestc.edu.cn</A>）下载区下载。</P>\r\n<P>（2）各学院在教师和学生中进行广泛的宣传发动。</P>\r\n<P>（3）各学院对学院参赛作品进行酝酿，进行选拔和预审。</P>\r\n<P>（4）各学院经过预审后向校团委报送已选定的学院参赛作品、《参赛作品汇总表》和《作品申报书》等文件。</P>\r\n<P>（5）学校成立专家评审委员会。</P>\r\n<P>2.书面复审阶段（4月11日——4月15日）</P>\r\n<P>由评审委员会对作品进行书面复审并确定终审决赛名单。</P>\r\n<P>3.终审准备阶段（4月15日——4月22日）</P>\r\n<P>进入终审名单的作品做好参加终审答辩的各项物资技术准备。</P>\r\n<P>4.终审阶段（4月23日——4月26日）</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;由评审委员会对作品进行终审，并由作者进行答辩或展示。 </P>\r\n<P>六、评审及奖励方式</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;1.评审方式</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 以作品的科学性、先进性、理论性和现实意义为基本标准，由各学院对上报作品进行预审，组委会办公室负责作品的资格审查，评审委员会进行书面复审和终审答辩，并确定奖励名单。</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;2.奖励方式</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;本次校内预选赛将按照以下三种方式进行奖励：</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;（1）、个人奖</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;大赛设特等奖2名、一等奖4名、二等奖6名、三等奖10名，分别发给奖金及荣誉证书；获特等、一等的作品将优先获得代表学校参加四川省及第十二届全国“挑战杯” 大学生课外学术科技作品竞赛的资格；</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;（2）、团体奖</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 获特等、一等、二等和三等者可以分别获得100分、70分、40分和20分的计分，大赛将以学院为单位，按照以上积分制产生团体金奖1个，银奖2个，铜奖3个。分别给予奖金并颁发荣誉证书；</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;（3）、组织奖</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 大赛将以各学院组织作品阶段的情况确定最佳组织奖两个。</P>\r\n<P>七、报名方式</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;1、本次大赛按照学院内部申请、内部预审的方式进行报名；</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;2、有意报名者需在创新创业中心网站上下载《作品申报书》（一式三份）后认真填写，在规定时间内将参赛作品及申报书上交至各学院分团委处；由各学院分团委组织开展预审后将选定的学院参赛作品及申报书上报至组委会（包括纸质档和电子档）。各学院推选作品原则上不超过15件，确有特别优秀的作品，可适当超报。</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;3、组委会办公室地址：清水河校区&nbsp; 学生活动中心104室<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </P>\r\n<P>联系人：杨明</P>\r\n<P>联系电话：61830553&nbsp;&nbsp; 13558806386</P>\r\n<P>咨询QQ：<A href="mailto:askinnovation@qq.com">askinnovation@qq.com</A><BR>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>八、其他要求</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;1、做好组织领导工作。各学院组织作品阶段要在学院党政领导的总体指导下进行，各学院开展和组织报送学生课外学术科技作品的情况将作为评选优秀组织奖的重要内容；</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;2、做好宣传发动工作。各学院要以本届“挑战杯”竞赛开展为契机，加大对“挑战杯”大学生课外学术科技作品竞赛的宣传力度，使广大学生更加充分了解“挑战杯”活动的意义、目的和要求，更加积极地参加“挑战杯”的各项赛事；</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;3、做好指导工作。各学院应注意吸引优秀教师积极参与指导这项工作，以保证学生作品的质量。<BR>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 电子科技大学创新创业中心</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2011年3月1日</P>\r\n<P><BR>《作品申报书》&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 请点击下载（右键另存为）或浏览:作品申报书.doc</P>\r\n<P>《参赛作品汇总表》请点击下载（右键另存为）或浏览:参赛作品汇总表.xls </P>\r\n<P>《参考资料》&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 请点击下载（右键另存为）或浏览:参考资料.rar</P>', 1044, 1299806987, '2011-03-10 17:29:47', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(639, 10, '创新基金申报事宜', '', NULL, 0, '<P>现将目前收集到的教师提供的创新基金的题目和要求向同学们公布，请大家按照学校的要求积极报名。如有意向，请自行组队（每队不超过三人），于3月16日之前把要申报的题目及学号、姓名、联系方式、负责人等几项信息发至邮箱<A href="mailto:zhaowenlimath@126.com">zhaowenlimath@126.com</A>。</P>\r\n<P>附：学校的通知文件</P>', 736, 1300073756, '2011-03-13 19:35:56', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(640, 15, '我校组织第九届ACM程序设计竞赛宣讲会', '', NULL, 0, '<P><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=512" align=baseline border=0></P>\r\n<P><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=513" align=baseline border=0></P>\r\n<P><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=511" align=baseline border=0></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 电子科技大学第九届ACM程序设计竞赛暨西南地区暨西南地区高校邀请赛开幕在即。3月10日下午，数学科学学院和校ACM队在清水河校区A204举办了本次比赛的宣讲会。<BR>讲座正式开始之前，校ACM队为同学们播放了精心制作的宣传视频，视频中介绍了校ACM队历年的辉煌战绩。在历数一个个奖项的同时，也进一步鼓动了大家参与ACM竞赛的积极性。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 本次宣讲会由校ACM队教练杨鹏老师和校ACM队队长廖洪舒同学主讲。杨鹏老师就历史发展、赛事结构等方面对ACM-ICPC（ACM国际大学生程序设计竞赛）进行了系统的介绍，并和大家分享了ACM-ICPC中一些有趣而吸引人的经历，使大家进一步地了解了这项全球性的竞赛。廖洪舒同学针对本次校ACM竞赛介绍了输入输出、算法的时间复杂度及其优化等问题，并介绍了本次比赛的流程和规则。最后，廖队长选取了三个有趣的思考题和台下的同学进行了互动，同学们积极思考，踊跃回答队长提出的问题，展示了同学们也将本次宣讲推向了高潮。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 宣讲会举行得非常成功，场面火爆。宣讲会结束后，一些意犹未尽的同学，还与教练和队长进行了单独的交流。关于如何自我提高，如何进入校ACM集训队，教练和队长一一进行了解答，并且鼓励大家通过刻骨的训练成为校队的一员。</P>', 1201, 1300250840, '2011-03-15 20:47:20', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
