"> <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">告</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">人</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">：</SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体" lang=EN-US> Prof. </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family:  @黑体 ; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">Min Tsao</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告地点</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">： 清水河校区主楼<SPAN lang=EN-US>A1-512<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告时间：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt" lang=EN-US>4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>27</SPAN>日（周三）上午<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>：<SPAN lang=EN-US>30<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告人简介：</SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US>Min Tsao</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US> </SPAN></FONT><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">于</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">1985</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">年在兰州大学获得学士学位；</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">1995</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">在加拿大西蒙菲莎大学获得统计学博士学位。现为加拿大维多利亚大学数学与统计系终身教授。主要研究兴趣为经验多半理论、稳健统计、数据分析、生物统计学、工程统计、医学统计等。已在</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">Annals of Statistics</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">、</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">Journal of Statistical Computation and Data Analysis</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">等国际知名学术期刊上发表论文三十余篇，现任</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">Canadian Journal of Statistics</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">副主编。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">报告摘要：</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">在这里我将讨论一个新的随机效应混合模型为基础的长时间序列聚类方法。本研究的问题来源于不列颠哥伦比亚省水电公司 </SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">(BC Hydro). </SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">此公司收集了一些客户能源消耗时间序列</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">(</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">负载序列</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">), </SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">希望用这些负载序列对客户进行分类</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">. </SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">客户分类牵扯到客户收费标准确定和水电公司发电能力规划等重要问题</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">. </SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">但用负载序列进行分类有两个技术困难：</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">[1] </SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">负载序列非常高维</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">; [2]</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">它们可能有复杂而重要的协方差结构。现有的聚类分析方法无法同时处理这些困难</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">. </SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">以随机效应混合模型为基础的长时间序列聚类方法对上述问题特别有效。随机效应混合模型基于组件层次模型。它采用高度灵活的时间序列协方差</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">antedependence</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">模型。我将讨论这种混合模型的构建，模型参数估计和它在聚类分析中的应用。这是一个统计学中</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">“</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">应用驱动研究</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">  </SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">的典型的例子。我希望通过这个例子来讲述目前北美统计学的一些发展趋势，并希望非统计学家也能对这些趋势讨论感兴趣。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 110%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 110%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt">欢迎全校师生参加！<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>', 895, 1303358924, '2011-04-20 20:08:44', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(673, 10, '期中考试安排', '', NULL, 0, '请同学们仔细核对考试的时间和地点。', 710, 1303438852, '2011-04-21 18:20:52', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(674, 10, '我校教授应邀在福建省线性代数、高等代数教学研讨会上做主题报告', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate w:st="on" Year="2011" Month="4" Day="23" IsLunarDate="False" IsROCDate="False"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">月</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>23</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">，受高等教育出版社和厦门大学等的邀请，我校黄廷祝教授出席了高等教育出版社与福建省高校联合主办的福建省高等代数、线性代数教学研讨会，并应邀做了大会主题报告。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">黄廷祝教授在题为</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">线性代数的教学与课程建设</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">的</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">报告中，从优化教学内容体系、教材建设、研究型教学方法、应用现代教育技术提升教学水平等几个方面报告了我校在相关课程教学方面的教学改革情况与经验。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', 610, 1303789718, '2011-04-25 19:48:38', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(675, 22, '第二届数学文化节拉开帷幕', '', NULL, 0, '<FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=537">&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman"><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=532">&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=533"></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=534"></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman"></FONT></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">4</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">25</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">日，电子科技大学第二届数学文化节拉开帷幕，系列活动将持续一周，内容涵盖数学文化图片展、数学应用领域名家讲座、题材影片放映、数字谜题晋级赛几个板块。旨在向全校师生展示数学学科的独特魅力，普及数学知识，解析数学思想，突显数学趣味。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman"><FONT size=3>本届文化节以中国传统数学的主要成就及发展史展示开篇，吸引了很多同学驻足观看。同时，现场进行趣味数学题有奖竞答活动，浅显生活化的题面，带着同学走进精彩神秘的数学天地。在活动现场，同学们或低头冥思，或写写画画，得到答案的满足，陷入沉思的焦灼让我们感受到在匆忙来往的行人之间显现出的思考的静谧之美。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman"><FONT size=3>本次活动由数学科学学院主办，学院研分会、学生会和党支部协办，在为我院师生就数学知识交流互动搭建平台的同时，也为广大数学爱好者进行学术交流、探索和学科知识积累提供了机会，激发了广大同学学习数学的兴趣，锻炼了大家的思维能力。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman"><FONT size=3>后续活动将如期开展，期待全校师生的积极参与。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman"><FONT size=3></FONT></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<DIV align=center>\r\n<TABLE style="WIDTH: 100%; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; mso-yfti-tbllook: 1184; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt" class=MsoNormalTable border=0 cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="100%">\r\n<TBODY>\r\n<TR style="HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-yfti-irow: 0; mso-yfti-firstrow: yes">\r\n<TD style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; WIDTH: 24.56%; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; HEIGHT: 14.25pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt solid; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-border-alt: solid windowtext .5pt" width="24%">\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">活动名称<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P></TD>\r\n<TD style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1pt solid; BORDER-LEFT: #f0f0f0; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent;