IZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">. </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">他和北京中科院数学院</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">, </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">九所</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">,</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">大连理工大学</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">,</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">复旦大学和香港中文大学有合作联系</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">. 2007 </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年被大连理工大学聘为海天学者</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">,</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">博导</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">;<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>2008 </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年起已在大工招收了三名博士生</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">. 98 </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年直今已成功指导了</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">10</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">位博士生完成学位，目前带有</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">5</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">名在读博士生。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">2010</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年被评为利物蒲大学</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">21</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">位跨学科领军</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">Champions</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">人才之一。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 110%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 110%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt">欢迎全校师生参加！<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>', 824, 1306202159, '2011-05-23 17:55:59', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(693, 11, '2011年毕业生基层就业学费补偿和贷款代偿的通知', '', NULL, 0, '<P>各同学：<BR>1、根据《高等学校毕业生学费和国家助学贷款代偿暂行办法》（财教[2009]15号）规定。高校毕业生到中西部地区和艰苦边远地区基层单位就业、服务期在3年以上(含3年)的，其学费和国家助学贷款由国家实行代偿，所需资金由中央财政安排。详细内容请见附件。<BR><BR>2、请各位同学仔细阅读和理解新政策，符合条件的学生须向学院提交：</P>\r\n<P>一、学生本人填写的《学费和国家助学贷款代偿申请表》（两份）；二、就业协议书（两份）；并填写《2011年第一批基层就业学费代偿贷款代偿汇总表》，请位同学于6月14日之前将各种资料备齐上交到学院学生科，汇总表须发送至<A href="mailto:yepy2007@126.com">yepy2007@126.com</A>，各类相关文件表格详见下载区，谢谢！<BR></P>', 735, 1306208174, '2011-05-23 19:36:14', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(694, 22, '2011第三届栋梁工程全国高校“栋梁之星”评选活动方案', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">一、活动背景及意义</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 15.5pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman " lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">“栋梁工程”是在四川省委、省政府的大力支持下，由四川省扶贫基金会联合有关单位面向全国发起的一项专门以品学兼优、家境贫寒的高校学生为援助对象的大型公益事业，至今已为遍布全国<SPAN lang=EN-US>200</SPAN>多所高校的四万多名学生提供了<SPAN lang=EN-US>2000</SPAN>—<SPAN lang=EN-US>20000</SPAN>元不等的经济援助，引起了省内外、海内外的广泛关注，产生了良好的社会效益。“栋梁工程”品牌已于<SPAN lang=EN-US>2003</SPAN>年获得国家商标局的注册保护。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">栋梁工程一直坚持 “援助明日栋梁，培育民族精英”的理念，坚持为国家培养人才、扶持人才。为在全国范围内选拔优秀高端人才，激励大学生刻苦学习、自强不息，开拓创新，同时发掘优秀创业项目，进一步在全国范围内宣传栋梁工程，充分展示栋梁工程十年成绩和效果，栋梁工程将于<SPAN lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN>年举办“第三届全国高校栋梁之星评选活动”。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><FONT size=3> “</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">栋梁之星”项目在栋梁工程事业中具有独特的地位和作用，是栋梁工程事业“金字塔”型社会效益的最高层，能集中凸显这项事业的巨大价值和长远意义。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">在栋梁工程<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>周年之际，计划在全国高校中评选出<SPAN lang=EN-US>50</SPAN>名“栋梁之星”，累计达到<SPAN lang=EN-US>130</SPAN>名，均获得由知名企业提供的奖学金，并将由党政领导、知名专家学者、企业总裁对其进行一对一的跟踪培养。在此基础上栋梁工程还将选拔高校学生报送的优秀创业项目，推荐给有投资意向的企业，为学生提供创业基金及专业人士的指导，从而实现大学生创业、就业的梦想。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">二、组织机构<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">主办单位：四川省扶贫基金会<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">承办单位：四川省扶贫基金会栋梁工程分会<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">评审委员会：知名高校专家教授，党政机关领导人，企业高管等权威人士组成评选审定委员会。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">官方网站：腾讯新闻网、腾讯栋梁工程微博、中国校媒网、各大高校校园网、四川省栋梁工程官方网站。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">三、报名条件<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">、普通高校的全日制本科生和研究生； <SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">、具有良好的思想政治素质，学业成绩优良，自强不息，品行端正，热心公益，乐观向上；<SPAN lang=EN-US> <o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">、勇于克服在学业、科研、生活或其他方面的困难，表现出非同一般的顽强毅力，有突出的自强事迹或个人成就。 <SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">（<SPAN style="BACKGROUND: yellow; mso-highlight: yellow">有独立策划、论证的，具有实施可行性的创业项目的同学优先</SPAN>选拔。）<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">四、活动内容及活动时间（<SPAN lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>月</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 黑体" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">—</FONT></SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman " lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年<SPAN lang=EN-US>8</SPAN>月）<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">、申报阶段<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">从<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>月初起，将在全国高校中启动“栋梁之星”评选活动。将有关通知传达到有关高校，由有关高校将活动内容和相关报名信息通知到各个院系，并通过高校网站、校园论坛、校园广播等渠道广为宣传。 <SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>日前由各高校收集、汇总“栋梁之星”的申请资料及创业项目计划书。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">、高校评审阶段<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate w:st="on" Year="2011" Month="6" Day="15" IsLunarDate="False" IsROCDate="False"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>6</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>15</SPAN>日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">前，以高校为单位对本校学生的综合情况和创业项目进行初审，筛选出<SPAN lang=EN-US>3-5</SPAN>名最优秀的学生资料，于<st1:chsdate w:st="on" Year="2011" Month="6" Day="25" IsLunarDate="False" IsROCDate="False"><SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>25</SPAN>日</st1:chsdate>前以邮寄方式报送栋梁工程。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">、专家评审阶段<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">“栋梁之星”专家评审团对各高校选送的栋梁之星参评对象和优秀的创业项目进行筛选和评审，最终确定<SPAN lang=EN-US>50</SPAN>名“栋梁之星”。其中优秀的创业项目推荐给有投资意向的企业，为学生提供创业基金及专业人士的指导，从而实现大学生创业、就业的梦想。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>4</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">、公告及表彰<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>7</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">月至<SPAN lang=EN-US>8</SPAN>月期间，通过媒体对外公告“栋梁之星”及“最佳创业项目”名单。获奖学生将在栋梁工程十周年总结表彰大会上获得表彰并授予“栋梁之星”称号及获得“栋梁之星”奖学金，同时有机会参加“栋梁工程发展高峰论坛暨青年学子交流大会”，并与香港、澳门的“未来之星”交流互动，与企业家交流学习。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">五、创业项目实施<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">通过评审委员会选拔的优秀创业项目，经专家和企业评估后，将以直接投资或合作开发方式对创业项目进行投资，或者协助学生对项目进行进一步研发和开发。学生独立运营创业项目的，企业有权对项目进行跟踪管理，对初期运行良好的项目可增加资金投入。创业项目也可由企业单独运营，学生享有收益分配权利。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">六、奖项设置<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">“栋梁之星”奖学金：<SPAN lang=EN-US>50</SPAN>名，每名学生获得奖学金<SPAN lang=EN-US>5000</SPAN>元</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: red; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">四川省扶贫基金会栋梁工程</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">分会联<SPAN style="COLOR: black">络人：陈娟、黄雪莲<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">联系电话：<SPAN lang=EN-US>028-86605289</SPAN>、<SPAN lang=EN-US>13408676479</SPAN>、<SPAN lang=EN-US>13683450356<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">传真：<SPAN lang=EN-US>028-86605090<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN>网址：<SPAN lang=EN-US><A href="http://www.donglianggc.org/"><FONT color=#0000ff>www.donglianggc.org</FONT></A><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">腾讯微博：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: #ff0080; FONT-SIZE: 15pt" lang=EN-US><A href="txfile:platformres:MsgMgrmsgmgr.htm">http://t.qq.com/donglianggc</A></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face="Times New Roman">联系地址：四川省成都市学道街<SPAN lang=EN-US>26</SPAN>号<SPAN lang=EN-US>701</SPAN>办公室<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN>邮编：<SPAN lang=EN-US>610016<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>', 770, 1306305053, '2011-05-24 22:30:53', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(695, 9, 'CSDN总裁蒋涛先生做客成电企业家讲坛', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate w:st="on" IsROCDate="False" IsLunarDate="False" Day="25" Month="5" Year="2011"><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>5</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>25</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">晚</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>7</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">点，数学科学学院承办的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>UESTC-CSDN</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">高校俱乐部成立仪式暨“激情与梦想，我的程序员之路”</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>—2011CSDN</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">全国高校巡讲，准时在图书馆二楼报告厅隆重召开。莅临本次讲坛的是</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>CSDN</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">总裁、中国计算机学会副秘书长、软件工程师工作委员会主任蒋涛先生。出席本次讲坛嘉宾有校团委娄春伟副书记，学院党委张泽宝副书记，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>CSDN</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">项目主管等。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"></SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman " lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=545"></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">讲坛第一部分是</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>UESTC-CSDN</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">高校俱乐部成立仪式，<st1:PersonName w:st="on" ProductID="蒋">蒋</st1:PersonName>先生为校</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>CSDN</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">俱乐部授牌并<st1:PersonName w:st="on" ProductID="向指导">向指导</st1:PersonName>老师颁发聘书。娄书记和张书记分别对我校成立</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>CSDN</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">俱乐部表示热烈的祝贺；并对我校学子提出“要想成为优秀的程序员，务必学好数学”的要求，希望学生充分利用</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>CSDN</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">资源，打造属于我们的俱乐部团队。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"></SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman " lang=EN-US><o:p><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=546"></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman " lang=EN-US><o:p><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=547"></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">讲坛第二部分是演讲环节，<st1:PersonName w:st="on" ProductID="蒋涛">蒋涛</st1:PersonName>先生就“</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>IT</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">行业发展趋势及其就业前景”进行了精彩的演讲，并热情饱满地向同学们介绍“企业用人要求，程序员所需素质及技能”；接下来的环节中给大学生的职业规划提出建议，指导同学们如何做好从学生到职业人的准备；最后，身为</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>CSDN</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">总裁的<st1:PersonName w:st="on" ProductID="蒋涛">蒋涛</st1:PersonName>先生深情并茂的向在座同学们分享自己的成功经验、成长历程，并给同学们提出三条建议“给做自己熟悉的，解决痛点；看大势；早动手”；互动环节使本次讲坛推向高潮，同学们的尖刻问题<st1:PersonName w:st="on" ProductID="和蒋">和蒋</st1:PersonName>先生的完美解答，令同学们颇受感慨，受益匪浅。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman " lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">学习成功人士经验，了解其成长历程，为成功打下基础。此次讲座的完满成功，不仅昭示着数学科学学院在信息计算领域的卓越表现，“</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>CSDN</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">高校俱乐部”成立更为学院的建设和同学们的发展提供了更好的平台。相信在学校和学院师生的共同努力下，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>CSDN</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">高校俱乐部有辉煌的明天。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=548"></SPAN></FONT><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman " lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', 869, 1306422761, '2011-05-26 07:12:41', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `article` (`articleid`, `sortid`, `title`, `source`, `author`, `userid`, `content`, `click`, `publish_time`, `launch_time`, `imageid`, `keyword1`, `keyword2`, `keyword3`) VALUES
(696, 22, '金山网络招聘信息', '', NULL, 0, '<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 金山网络将于本周六（5月28日）在清水河校区学生活动中心2楼圆厅召开2011年实习生及应届生招聘宣讲，主要面对<B>大三、研一、研二的实习生</B>，<B>提供产品、技术岗位（JAVA,C++,手机研发）的实习</B>，同时欢迎<B>应届生</B>，<B>不限专业（免费提供食宿，往返车费以及千元以上每月助学金）</B>，欢迎2011,2012届同学，现场参加笔试与面试。</SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt"></SPAN></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt"></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt">岗位介绍（<SPAN lang=EN-US>以下职位均接受2011、2012年毕业生</SPAN>）：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>岗位名称：</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: windowtext">助理产品运营经理</SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>试题类型：</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: windowtext" lang=EN-US><SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: windowtext">产品类</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>需求人数：</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: windowtext" lang=EN-US>10</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN>人</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="COLOR: blue">工作地点：</SPAN></B><SPAN>北京</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>工作职责：</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN>（协助产品运营经理进行以下工作）</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN>、调查和研究客户需求及行为模式，进行需求调研、研讨、分析；</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN>、进行产品详细特性规划和产品设计，并协助开发团队理解和掌握需求；</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN>、制定产品的营销推广方案，并参与和推动产品的实施推广；</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN><SPAN>、对新技术、国内外相关产品、相关体系进行研究，提出新产品建设思路和方向，组织立项，发展新产品；</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN><SPAN>、同开发团队、测试团队和实施团队紧密合作，共同推动产品发展。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>任职资格：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 0cm; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN>1、</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN>大学本科或以上学历，理工科；</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 0cm; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN>2、</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN>严谨的逻辑思维能力，对数据敏感，良好的分析问题解决问题的能力；</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN>、喜欢尝试各种互联网产品；</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN><SPAN>、优秀的沟通和表达能力，一定的人际关系发展能力；</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN><SPAN>、有参加过一些商业项目、软件项目或大学生实践活动的优先</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>岗位名称：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN>反病毒工程师</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>试题类型：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN>反病毒</SPAN><SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>需求人数：</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-WEIGHT: normal" lang=EN-US><SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>10</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black">人</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="COLOR: blue">工作地点：</SPAN></B><SPAN>珠海</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>工作职责：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>1.</SPAN><SPAN>样本鉴定；</SPAN><SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>2.</SPAN><SPAN>分析病毒样本并提供解决方案；</SPAN><SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>3.</SPAN><SPAN>信息安全技术研究。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>任职资格：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>1.</SPAN><SPAN>大学本科或以上学历；</SPAN><SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>2.</SPAN><SPAN>热爱底层开发工作，对反病毒</SPAN><SPAN>.</SPAN><SPAN>逆向工程、系统漏洞等有强烈兴趣；</SPAN><SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>3.</SPAN><SPAN>熟悉</SPAN><SPAN>x86</SPAN><SPAN>系列汇编语言，能熟练读懂汇编代码；</SPAN><SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN><SPAN>.</SPAN><SPAN>具有</SPAN><SPAN>C/C++</SPAN><SPAN>程序开发经验者优先。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>岗位名称：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN>客户端开发</SPAN><SPAN>工程师</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>试题类型：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN>C++</SPAN><SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>需求人数：</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: windowtext; FONT-WEIGHT: normal" lang=EN-US>15</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN>人</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="COLOR: blue">工作地点：</SPAN></B><SPAN>珠海、北京</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>工作职责：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>信息安全软件产品的开发。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>任职资格：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>1.</SPAN><SPAN>大学本科或以上学历；</SPAN><SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>2.</SPAN><SPAN>熟练掌握</SPAN><SPAN>C++</SPAN><SPAN>，并对其它开发语言有所了解；</SPAN><SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>3.</SPAN><SPAN>理解</SPAN><SPAN>windows</SPAN><SPAN>操作系统基本原理；</SPAN><SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>4.</SPAN><SPAN>具备较好的英语读写能力，能无障碍阅读</SPAN><SPAN>MSDN</SPAN><SPAN>等技术文档；</SPAN><SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>5.</SPAN><SPAN>具有强烈的团队意识，善于沟通交流；</SPAN><SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>6.</SPAN><SPAN>具有安全相关软件开发经验，熟悉</SPAN><SPAN>PKI</SPAN><SPAN>机制者优先。</SPAN><SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>&nbsp;</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>&nbsp;</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>岗位名称：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN>服务端开发</SPAN><SPAN>工程师</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>试题类型：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>JAVA</SPAN><SPAN>、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>PHP<SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>需求人数：</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: windowtext; FONT-WEIGHT: normal" lang=EN-US>10</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN>人</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="COLOR: blue">工作地点：</SPAN></B><SPAN>珠海、北京</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>工作职责：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>信息安全软件产品的开发。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>任职资格：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 0cm; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm" class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>1.</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN>大学本科或以上学历；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>2..</SPAN><SPAN>精通</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>Java.PHP </SPAN><SPAN>语言中的任意一种，理解面向对象思想，熟练使用标准库；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>3.</SPAN><SPAN>熟练使用常用数据结构和算法；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>4.</SPAN><SPAN>了解</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>SQL</SPAN><SPAN>，至少使用过一种数据库；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>5.</SPAN><SPAN>热爱软件开发工作，具有较好的沟通和协作能力，熟练阅读英文技术文档；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR><BR></SPAN><SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>岗位名称：</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: windowtext; FONT-WEIGHT: normal">手机</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN>开发</SPAN><SPAN>工程师</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>试题类型：</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: windowtext; FONT-WEIGHT: normal" lang=EN-US>ANDROID</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: windowtext; FONT-WEIGHT: normal">或</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: windowtext; FONT-WEIGHT: normal" lang=EN-US>IOS</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>需求人数：</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-WEIGHT: normal" lang=EN-US>20</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black">人</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="COLOR: blue">工作地点：</SPAN></B><SPAN>北京</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>工作职责：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN>、负责</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>Android</SPAN><SPAN>或</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>iOS</SPAN><SPAN>平台的应用软件开发；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>2</SPAN><SPAN>、编写项目设计，实现和测试文档；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>3</SPAN><SPAN>、编写和执行项目的单元测试和质量控制。</SPAN><SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN>任职资格：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 0cm; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN>1.</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN>大学本科或以上学历，计算机或相关专业；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>2.</SPAN><SPAN>扎实的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>C++</SPAN><SPAN>或</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>Object-C</SPAN><SPAN>或</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>java</SPAN><SPAN>语言基础，熟悉网络开发；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>3.</SPAN><SPAN>有</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>ANDROID</SPAN><SPAN>或</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>iPhone</SPAN><SPAN>开发经验者优先；</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>4.</SPAN><SPAN>热爱手机软件开发，工作认真负责，较好的沟通能力和独立开发能力。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 0cm; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm" class=MsoNormal><SPAN></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 0cm; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm" class=MsoNormal><SPAN></SPAN>&nbsp;</P><SPAN>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt">金山网络暑期训练营七月开营啦</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>~</SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt">海量实习岗位虚位以待 &nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>训练营类别：<B>技术达人训练营</B>、<B>产品大师训练营</B></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>训练营模式：精英式培养模式、业内资深人士全程辅导</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>训练营文化：大五文化</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>训练营宗旨：根据营员自身技术基础制定未来发展方向</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN>训练营福利：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN>、为营员每月提供补贴</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>2</SPAN><SPAN>、提供免费三餐、提供住宿</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>3</SPAN><SPAN>、报销学校至公司的往返路费</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>4</SPAN><SPAN>、每周考核前三名奖励公司小礼品、每月评选最具影响力“每月一星”</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>5</SPAN><SPAN>、考核符合金山网络人才标准，可转为金山网络正式员工</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>&nbsp;更多详细介绍：<A href="http://xy.ijinshan.com/" target=_blank>xy.ijinshan.com</A></SPAN></SPAN></P></SPAN>', 877, 1306461736, '2011-05-26 18:02:16', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(697, 9, '数学科学学院2011暑期社会实践启动', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>26</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">日下午</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>4</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>30</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">，数学科学学院</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">年暑期社会实践动员大会在教学楼</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>B309</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">顺利召开，学院党委张泽宝副书记亲临现场给同学们予以指导，大会由学院分团委书记李坤龙老师主持。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=549"></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=550"></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: 10.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"><FONT face=Calibri>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">首先张书记对学院本科学生工作的规划、工作的重点做了简单的阐述，要求学生们要结合学院专业特色，立定坚定目标，为之不懈奋斗，做到爱班、爱院、爱学校；临近四六级考试和期末考试，希望同学们抓紧时间，合理规划，做最后</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>20</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">天冲刺，争取在考试中取得优异成绩。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">&nbsp;接下来李老师对</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">年暑期社会实践做了详细的部署，动员会是为了让学生们更好地了解社会实践活动，以及即将到来的暑假中，更好地进行社会实践活动。李老师条理清晰而又详尽地向大家介绍有关暑期社会实践的新动向和流程，如组建团队、确立项目、申报、上交材料、总结资料等等；阐述了暑期社会实践的重大意义，给同学们的暑期社会实践活动表明了方向，开拓了思路，更激发了同学们参与暑期社会实践活动的积极性。</SPAN></FONT></P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri , sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">此次暑期社会实践动员大会的召开，拉开了我们数学科学学院暑期社会实践活动的序幕，为接下来的各项工作的展开奠定了坚实的基础。相信，我院</SPAN><FONT face=宋体><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri , sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA" lang=EN-US> 2011</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">年的暑期社会实践将顺利地进行，圆满地完成，并且会涌现一批优秀的社会实践团队和个人。</SPAN></FONT></FONT> ', 797, 1306552563, '2011-05-27 19:16:03', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(698, 10, '关于2007级毕业设计答辩准备PPT的通知', '', NULL, 0, '同学们请注意：毕业设计答辩定为6月9日星期四全天，答辩时间为15---20分钟，每个同学准备5---7分钟PPT，答辩地点另行通知。', 961, 1306734277, '2011-05-29 21:44:37', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(699, 11, '又是一年毕业时，文明离校倡导会', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>5.31</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">日下午</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2:30</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">，数学科学学院在教学楼</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>A102</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">教室召开毕业生文明离校倡导会，会议由张娇老师主持。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=551"></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 15.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><FONT size=3>首先张老师就今年的毕业生党员组织关系转接问题、助学贷款还贷事项作了详细的讲解，其次针对毕业生就业派遣档案和户口迁移等相关问题作了具体的强调，要求同学们信息填报务必准确和完整，以免给后续工作带来不必要的麻烦。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><FONT size=3>最后倡导大家安全文明离校，抱着一颗感恩的心，给学弟学妹们留下好的印象；另外强调外出或者聚餐的时候注意人身财产安全。留下一个安全、洁净的环境给母校。</FONT></SPAN></P>', 770, 1306899554, '2011-05-31 19:39:14', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(700, 11, '爱心圆梦，就业双选—数学科学学院川师行', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">为了切实做好高校毕业生就业指导工作，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> <SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">月</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">31</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">日上午，我院本科生和研究生未就业团体在校团委刘莹老师的带队下前往四川师范大学狮子山校区，参加由团省委等单位主办的“爱心圆梦”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">--</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">四川省大学生就业创业专场双选会，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">600</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">余家企业单位为未就业大学生提供</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">10000</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">余个招聘岗位和</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">2000</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">余个就业创业见习岗位。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">本次双选会单位包含了中国银行、百度、新东方等多家国际知名企业，提供技术顾问、人事经理、财务主管、销售副总、酒店柜员等职位，迎合了不同层次和能力的毕业生的需求。我院学生针对自己的求职意向与用人单位详细的交流，了解岗位的发展空间和薪酬待遇，认真的投送每一份简历，踏实的走好自己的求职之路。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman "><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=552"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman "><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=553"></SPAN></P><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN>', 977, 1306899638, '2011-05-31 19:40:38', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `article` (`articleid`, `sortid`, `title`, `source`, `author`, `userid`, `content`, `click`, `publish_time`, `launch_time`, `imageid`, `keyword1`, `keyword2`, `keyword3`) VALUES
(701, 9, '书山揽胜 学海荡舟─ 图书馆服务校园行', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt">为更好地满足全校师生对图书、文献资源的需求，图书馆将开展以“服务进学院 资源助科研”为主题的服务校园行活动，旨在与各学院</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">增进联系，提高服务质量、响应速度，缩短服务距离。更好的</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt">融入教学科研。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p><FONT face=宋体></FONT></o:p></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 0cm; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">&Oslash;<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt Times New Roman">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 华文琥珀; COLOR: #c00000; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">服务之一：你选书我买单 — 经费进学院 支持学院学科资源建设 </SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: #c00000; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">图书馆拨专款用于学院学科资源建设，已订学科专业图书将纳入图书馆馆藏，学院师生享有</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 华文琥珀; COLOR: #4a442a; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">优先借阅权</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 35.45pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 7.1pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; COLOR: #4c4c4c; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">详情请</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">咨询：</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>61831793</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">李老师</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><FONT face=Calibri> <SPAN lang=EN-US>61831883</SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">杨老师</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Email: reader@uestc.edu.cn<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: -21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt -220.9pt; mso-char-indent-count: -2.0; mso-para-margin-left: -23.04gd" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><FONT face=Calibri><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: -21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21pt; 