family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">）</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">数据库的论文检索报告，包括论文收录和引用，为科研人员的职称评定、各类人才计划申报，奖励申报等提供信息服务。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 42pt; MARGIN: 0cm 21pt 0pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 4.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">详情请咨询</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">：</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>83202340</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">朱老师</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>jiansuo@uestc.edu.cn<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">服务承诺：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">您通过电子邮箱（非涉密课题）、拷贝等方式提交的查新委托和检索委托，我们当天进行响应。查新报告的完成时间：国内为<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>个工作日内，国内外查为<SPAN lang=EN-US>14</SPAN>个工作日内；一般检索报告在<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>个工作日内。如果您有加急需求，可以通过邮件、电话、<SPAN lang=EN-US>QQ</SPAN>等方式进行说明或咨询。我们会尽力缩短服务周期，提供优质、高效的服务。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #c00000; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: -21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1" class=MsoListParagraph><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">&Oslash;<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt Times New Roman">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 华文琥珀; COLOR: #c00000; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">服务之五：学科资源统计——为学科评估提供支撑<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 23.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">提供馆藏学科资源统计，为学院学科专业认证评估、学科点申报提供支撑材料。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 36.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 3.5" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">详情请咨询：</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>61831793</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">李老师</SPAN><FONT face=Calibri><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US> binli@uestc.edu.cn</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 99.75pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 9.5" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>61831799 </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">秦老师</SPAN><FONT face=Calibri><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"> <SPAN lang=EN-US>qinh@uestc.edu.cn</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: -21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1" class=MsoListParagraph><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">&Oslash;<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt Times New Roman">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 华文琥珀; COLOR: #c00000; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">服务之六：数字资源专题讲座<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 20.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">提供特定数字资源的使用培训，用户可选择与本学院相关的某个数字资源，由图书馆联系图书馆商提供专题培训讲座服务，仅限图书馆引进的数字资源。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 20.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: -21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1" class=MsoListParagraph><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-family: Wingdings" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">&Oslash;<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt Times New Roman">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 华文琥珀; COLOR: #c00000; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">服务之七：数字资源评价与推荐<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 20.15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">图书馆欢迎广大师生对已引进和正在试用的数字资源提供评价意见，以及对未引进资源进行推荐，以帮助我们更好地开展数字资源引进工作。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 20.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 42.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 4.05" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">详情请咨询：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>61831766</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">　秦老师</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri> 61830132 </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">毕老师　</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>Email: qinh@uestc.edu.cn</FONT></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face=Calibri>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;