i-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">年</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri , sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA" lang=EN-US>4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">月</SPAN> ', 566, 1306982044, '2011-06-01 18:34:04', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(704, 12, '香港大学数学系Wai-Ki CHING博士学术讲座', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: -77pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 105.05pt; mso-para-margin-left: 2.67gd; mso-char-indent-count: -5.5; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告题目</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">On <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>High-dimensional <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>Markov <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>Chain <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>Models <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>with Applications<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: -77pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 105.05pt; mso-para-margin-left: 2.67gd; mso-char-indent-count: -5.5; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">告</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">人</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">：</SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体" lang=EN-US>Dr. Wai-Ki <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>CHING</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">报告地点</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">：清水河校区主楼<SPAN lang=EN-US>A1-512<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">报告时间：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">6</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">月 <SPAN lang=EN-US>13</SPAN>日（周一）下午<SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN>：<SPAN lang=EN-US>30<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告摘要：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">Markov chain models are commonly used to model categorical data sequences. In this talk, we present<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>some high-dimensional Markov chain model for modelling categorical data sequences. In particular, both high-order Markov chain models and multivariate Markov chain models will be presented. Estimation methods for the model parameters will be proposed with examples of practical applications.<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告人简介：</SPAN><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">Wai-Ki Ching is an </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">Associate</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN"> Professor (with tenure) in the Department of Mathematics at the University of Hong Kong. He obtained his B. Sci. (Hons) and M. Phil. degrees from the University of Hong Kong in 1991 and 1994 respectively. He then received his Ph.D. degree from the Chinese University of Hong Kong in 1998. He was a visiting post-doc Fellow at the Cambridge University in 1999. Before taking up the lectureship at his Alma Mater in 2001, he was a lecturer in the Faculty of Mathematical Studies at the University of Southampton (2000-2001). He was awarded the Best Student Paper Prize (2nd Prize) in the Copper Mountain Conference (Colorado University and SIAM) U.S.A. (1998), the Outstanding Ph.D. Thesis Prize in the Engineering Faculty, the Chinese University of Hong Kong, Hong Kong (1998), the Certificate of Merit in the IEEE (Hong Kong Section) Postgraduate Student Paper Contest, Hong Kong (1998) and the Croucher Foundation Fellowship, Hong Kong (1999).<o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 26.25pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">Ching’s research focus is Mathematical Modeling and Applied Computing. In particular, the applications of stochastic models and numerical algorithms in solving problems related to Markov chains, bioinformatics, complex systems, data mining, epidemiology, financial mathematics and game theory. He is an author/editor of more than 200 publications including 3 books, 5 edited journal special issues, over 120 refereed journal papers, over 40 refereed book chapters and over 50 conference proceeding papers. Ching has reviewed papers for more than 60 different international journals. Currently, he is on the editorial board of </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: italic" lang=EN-US>Advances in Decision Sciences</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">,</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: italic" lang=EN-US>International Journal of Intelligent Engineering Informatics </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">and </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: italic" lang=EN-US>East Asian Journal on Applied</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN" lang=EN-US> </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: italic" lang=EN-US>Mathematics</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">. He has been the chief editor of </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: italic" lang=EN-US>Mathematical Modelling and Applied Computing </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">(2006-2009) and associate editor of </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-style: italic" lang=EN-US>Journal of Applied Mathematics and Decision Sciences </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: CMR12; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN">(2006-2009). He has obtained over 1.88 millions HK dollars research grants as the principal investigator (including RGC Competitive Earmarked Research Grants, External Consultancy Grants, Hung Hing Ying Physical Research Grants and Learnet Grant), and over 2.00 millions HK dollars as a co-investigator.</SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 110%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 110%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt">欢迎全校师生参加！<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>', 895, 1307504133, '2011-06-07 19:35:33', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `article` (`articleid`, `sortid`, `title`, `source`, `author`, `userid`, `content`, `click`, `publish_time`, `launch_time`, `imageid`, `keyword1`, `keyword2`, `keyword3`) VALUES
(705, 11, '数学科学学院学生会换届落下帷幕', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=554"></FONT></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3 face=Calibri><SPAN lang=EN-US><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=555"></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>6</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>13</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">日下午，数学科学学院学生会换届选举大会在品学楼</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>A304</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">顺利召开，参加本次大会的有学院张泽宝副书记，院分团委书记李坤龙，辅导员叶谱英和张娇老师，现任学生会的主席团与各部长以及所有学生会成员。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman " lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">本次换届选举大会是学院新届学生会竞选的第三个环节</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>——</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">竞选演讲板块。大会开始，现任学生会主席诸程翔宣布八位竞选者依次上台演讲，竞选者轮流走上讲台，为自身所竞选的职位做最后的演讲。面对台下众多评委与同学们的目光，场面热烈，特别是在演讲结束后的评委提问环节，综合考核了各位竞选者的临场应变能力。竞选结果由各位评委的打分决定产生，由分团委书记李老师宣布竞选名单。竞选结果确定了新一届数学科学学院学生会主席团的组成人员，他们分别是主席兼分团委副书记卢杰，副主席刘暠晟和任媛，各部长的安排将在主席团进一步商议之后公布。最后张书记总结讲话，首先祝贺本次学生会换届选举的成功进行，也对新一届学生会主席团的成员表示祝贺，对上一届学生会成员表示感谢，并发表了自己对学生会构建的一些看法和对新一届学生会的期待。</SPAN><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman " lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 7.8pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT size=3>换届大会的圆满结束，昭示着数学科学学院新一届学生会成立。最终获得主席团提名的各位竞选者经过三轮严厉的考核，成为我们新一届学生会的领导班子。相信在接下来一年当中，在分团委的带领下，我们学院新一届的学生会能够取得更加优异的成果，为学院的特色构建做出更大的贡献。</FONT></SPAN><A name=_GoBack></A><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman " lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', 816, 1307981982, '2011-06-13 08:19:42', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(706, 9, '数学科学学院在“颂歌献给党”歌咏比赛中荣获佳绩', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=556"></FONT></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=557"></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>6</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>14</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">日下午</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">时，电子科技大学庆祝中国共产党成立</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>90</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">周年“颂歌献给党”歌咏比赛在“成电会堂”隆重举行，数学科学学院代表队在此次歌咏赛中（清水河片区）荣获第四名的佳绩，授予三等奖表彰。合唱队由学院领导、党员老师及党员学生组成，演唱中热情昂扬、激情澎湃，勇创佳绩。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">赛前经过一系列精心的服装设计、演员上妆以及彩排活动，休息室中各位即将登台的队员们热情高涨，准备工作进行得如火如荼。此次合唱比赛我院合唱团演唱《七律</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>·</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">长征》与《长江之歌》两首曲目，在灯光及其背景的映衬下，合唱团在舞台上豪情万丈，唱出了磅礴的气势、宏伟的气魄，唱出了我们的青春活力和真情实感。更有观众拍手称赞道：“这样唱红歌才有气魄”，合唱结束后，台下响起雷鸣般的掌声。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">此次歌咏比赛旨在隆重庆祝建党</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>90</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">周年，同时数学科学学院在本场比赛中取得的圆满成功，不仅在丰富学院文化生活中取得了优秀成果，还充分展示了我院师生们的卓越精神风貌。相信在本月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>30</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">日的汇演中，数学科学学院合唱队再创佳绩。</SPAN></FONT></P>', 850, 1308064641, '2011-06-14 07:17:21', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(707, 11, '电子科技大学数学科学学院四年级本科生奖励办法', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">现将<SPAN lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN>年毕业生奖励评定工作安排通知如下：<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">一、时间安排： <SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 8.8pt; mso-para-margin-left: .84gd" class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">、<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>15</SPAN>日<SPAN lang=EN-US>-17</SPAN>日下午16：30之前：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">学生个人提出申请，向学院提交书面《电子科技大学四年级本科生奖励申请表》。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 8.8pt; mso-para-margin-left: .84gd" class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">、<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>17</SPAN>日<SPAN lang=EN-US>-20</SPAN>日：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" cl