HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">二、注意事项：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 12pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">、优秀本科毕业论文奖、就业奖由学校按文件统一表彰、发奖，不需学生个人申请、学院上报。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"> <SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 12pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 30.0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family:  Times New Roman " lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore"><FONT face="Times New Roman">2、</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">除院级奖励需结合学生的表现和获得的各种奖励进行评定之外，其他各奖项的</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">支持材料（获奖情况及证书复印件）有效时间为：<SPAN lang=EN-US>2010</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>9</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>日至<SPAN lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>20</SPAN>日</SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 12pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 30.0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"></SPAN></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">附：电子科技大学数学科学学院四年级本科生奖励办法</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 电子科技大学四年级本科生奖励申请表<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>', 1274, 1308130527, '2011-06-15 01:35:27', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(708, 9, '学院召开2011届毕业生座谈会', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=center><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=558"></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>6</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>17</SPAN>日上午，数学科学学院召开了以“收获、感恩、立业、奉献”为主题的<SPAN lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN>届毕业生座谈会。学校副校长余敏明、学院领导、教师代表出席了座谈会。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><FONT size=3>座谈会上，毕业生同学们结合自己在校期间的经历和感受，畅谈大学生活，分享收获，展望未来。同学们表达了学校、学院和老师们的感激之情，就学校、学院的发展以及同学们成长成才过程中遇到的问题提出了解决的方案和建议，并纷纷表示在以后的工作和生活中会更加勤奋，努力做出成绩，争取早日回报母校和社会。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><FONT size=3>余敏明副校长向同学们顺利完成学业表示祝贺，并以学长的身份与同学们分享了自己大学期间的学习和生活体会，希望同学们将来无论是走上工作岗位还是继续深造学习，都能重视团队精神，学会沟通、交流、理解和支持，做到“自强、感恩、包容、慈善”，在走出学校以后能与学校和老师保持紧密联系，将一些好的建议及时反馈给母校。黄廷祝院长也给予毕业生们真诚的祝福，希望同学们在今后学习、工作和生活中能够做到真诚待人、踏实做事。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>', 770, 1308294711, '2011-06-16 23:11:51', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(712, 10, '2010-2011-2学期数学科学学院期末考试安排', '', NULL, 0, '<FONT size=5>同学们，请相互转告。</FONT>', 546, 1308406314, '2011-06-18 06:11:54', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(714, 10, '数学学院举行本科生研究训练学术报告会', '', NULL, 0, '<P><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=564"></P>\r\n<P><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=566"></P>\r\n<P><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=565"></P>\r\n<P><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=568"></P>\r\n<P><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=567"></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate w:st="on" Year="2011" Month="6" Day="16" IsLunarDate="False" IsROCDate="False"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>6</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">月</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>16</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">下午，数学学院举行了第一次本科生研究训练学术报告会。学校学生处吕红胤处长、教务处余魅副处长受邀到场指导，黄廷祝院长、孙清平书记、高建副院长、张泽宝副书记、科研训练部分导师及</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>28</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">、</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>29</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">级同学参加了报告会。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">黄廷祝院长、吕红胤处长、余魅副处长分别进行了讲话，强调了科研训练对培养</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">创新</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">人才</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">的重要意义，</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">肯定了数学学院实行本科生研究导师制以来所取得的成绩，并鼓励同学们积极参加科研训练、参与各种课外科技活动，</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">培养创新意识与创新能力。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>29</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">级的</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Verdana &#718;&#805; ">黄家东</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">、</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Verdana &#718;&#805; ">陈攀</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">、<SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">田玲玲</SPAN>同学，<SPAN lang=EN-US>28</SPAN>级的王迎春</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">同学分别做了题为</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">“非线性方程组的牛顿迭代算法改良”、“<SPAN lang=EN-US>Gauss-Codazzi</SPAN>方程的推导”、“<SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"> 基于博弈模型的多智能体覆盖控制</SPAN>”、“<SPAN lang=EN-US> n</SPAN>维欧式空间一类特殊集合的维数和势”</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">的学术报告。在报告中，同学们汇报了自己在科研导师的指导下所做的研究工作及部分成果。在提问环节，老师、同学的提问及敏锐的回答，既活跃了现场气氛又使在场的同学开阔了视野，获益匪浅。</SPAN><U><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></U></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">数学学院</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">从</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">年开始，将科研实训作为实习实训的必修内容列入培养方案，</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">制定并开始执行了《</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">本科生</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">科研实训</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">的内容、规范和要求<SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">》，已为</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" lang=EN-US>80</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">多名大二、大三的学生配备了科研导师。导师与学生经常见面，了解学习状况，提供学习资料，定期研讨。</SPAN></FONT></P>', 1206, 1308536547, '2011-06-19 18:22:27', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
