(717, 12, '上海交通大学方北香副教授学术讲座', '', NULL, 0, '<P>报告人：方北香（上海交通大学）<BR>题目：Global Uniqueness of Steady Transonic Shocks in Two--Dimensional<BR>Compressible Euler Flows<BR>时间：7月5日（周二）下午2:30-3:30<BR>地点：主楼A1-512<BR>摘要：In the famous book “Supersonic Flow and Shock Waves” by R. Courant and<BR>K.O. Friedrichs, it is indicated the existence of some special transonic<BR>shock solutions for the 2-D steady full Euler system. For instance, the<BR>transonic shock in supersonic flow past a wedge, the normal transonic shock<BR>in a straight duct, etc. The existence is obtained under assumptions that<BR>the solution is piecewise constant. In this talk, we will show that for the<BR>transonic shock solutions of wedge case, the special solutions are unique<BR>under some assumptions weaker than the piecewise constant assumption, which<BR>mainly include piecewise $C^1$ smooth, full subsonic flow field behind the<BR>shock front, as well as appropriate conditions on the tip of wedge and at<BR>infinity of the downstream subsonic flow.<BR>This is a joint work with Li LIU and Hairong YUAN.</P>\r\n<P>报告人简介：<BR>方北香，1978年出生，上海交通大学副教授；2000.7.和2005.7.在复旦大学分别获得学士和博士学位，导师为著名数学家陈恕行教授；2005.7.-2007.7.在上海交通大学作博士后研究；主要研究方向为高维守恒律、偏微分方程、流体力学中的数学问题等；作为短期访问学者先后访问美国Northwestern<BR>University 三次，及香港中文大学、德国University of Konstan等；在国外一流SCI刊物 Dis. Con. Dyn.<BR>Sys. -A、J. Differential Equations<BR>等上发表学术论文多篇；作为负责人承担了国家自然科学基金数学天元青年基金、国家自然科学基金青年基金等。</P>', 774, 1308705485, '2011-06-21 17:18:05', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(718, 12, '美国莱丝大学印卧涛博士学术讲座', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: -77pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 105.05pt; mso-para-margin-left: 2.67gd; mso-char-indent-count: -5.5; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告题目</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">：</SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 微软雅黑; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN"><FONT face="Times New Roman">Some<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Recent <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>Sparse <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>Optimization <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>Work <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: -7pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 105.05pt; mso-para-margin-left: 9.34gd; mso-char-indent-count: -.5; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 微软雅黑; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN"><FONT face="Times New Roman">at <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN>Rice University<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: -77pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 105.05pt; mso-para-margin-left: 2.67gd; mso-char-indent-count: -5.5; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">告</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> <SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">人</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman">：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt">印卧涛 博士</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">报告地点</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">： 清水河校区主楼<SPAN lang=EN-US>A1-512<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">报告时间：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt" lang=EN-US>6</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>30</SPAN>日（周四）上午<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>：0<SPAN lang=EN-US>0<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告人简介：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">Dr. Yin works as assistant professor at Rice University, Department of Computational and Applied Mathematics. The research of his group focuses on inverse problems arising in compressed sensing, image acquisition and processing, machine learning, computer vision, etc. Solving these problems requires appropriate regularization, and results in large-scale optimization and/or PDE problems. Subsequently our research is devoted to developing regularization models for ill-posed inverse problems and devising efficient numerical methods for solving them in practice. <o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">He received a bachelor’s degree in mathematics from Nanjing University in 2001. He earned a master’s degree in operations research from Columbia University in 2003; in 2006 he was awarded a second master’s degree and a doctorate, both in operations research. While studying at Columbia, He worked as a researcher in optimization for medical imaging and computer vision for Siemens Corporate Research, located in Princeton, New Jersey.<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; TEXT-INDENT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">报告摘要：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">This talk will give an overview of compressive sensing, as well as recent sparse optimization work done at Rice University. It includes (i) L1 optimization algorithms for general, as well as special, signals and sensing modalities, (ii) joint sparsity algorithms, (iii) improved algorithms such as those based on Bregman iterations and support detection, and (iv) matrix low-rank, matrix completion, and matrix factorization algorithms. Various applications<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">of these algorithms will be given.<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">The talk includes joint work with Prof. Yin Zhang (Rice), Dr. Yingying Li (Rice &amp; U.Houston), Dr. Yilun Wang (joining UESTC), Dr. Zaiwen Wen (SH Jiaotong), Dr. Junfeng Yang (Nanjing), and graduate students Wei Deng, Nabor Reyna, and Yangyang Xu.<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 15pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman">欢迎全校师生参加！</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>', 908, 1308705624, '2011-06-21 17:20:24', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(719, 10, '科研实训报名表&个人学习计划表', '', NULL, 0, '<P>各位同学：</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;科研导师的个人简介均已发布在学院橱窗内，请同学们前往查看。在6月28日（下周二）之前将报名表发至邮箱：<A href="mailto:zhaowenlimath@126.com">zhaowenlimath@126.com</A>。</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 另：请大家认真、详细地制定个人学习计划表，于下学期开学的第一周之内以班级为单位交至教务科周海波老师处。</P>', 880, 1308715556, '2011-06-21 20:05:56', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(720, 22, '“数科人在海外”第二期交流活动圆满成功', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang=EN-US><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=570"></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang=EN-US></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal align=left><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang=EN-US><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=569"></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang=EN-US></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast" lang=EN-US>6</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>22</SPAN>日下午<SPAN lang=EN-US>2:30</SPAN>，数学科学学院研究生科技文化活动——“数科人在海外” 留学交流沙龙第二期成功举办。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast"><FONT size=3>继第一期新加坡义安理工交流会后，同学们对此活动反响热烈。经过前期筹备，第二期交流会邀请到学院向昭银和武德安两位老师与同学们分享海外学习生活的体会和经验。两位老师分别在美国和日本有过留学经历，从准备出国到顺利成行，从初涉异域到学成归来，个中感悟颇为丰富。他们以“留学生活的零零碎碎”、“多元文化中成长”为主题与同学展开了讨论，详细介绍了海外高校的学术氛围、科研情况等，并对如何申请国外高校和奖学金、怎样尽快适应国外学习和生活模式等同学们关注的问题给出了中肯的建议。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><FONT size=3>通过此类活动，学院整合资源，营造氛围，多途径地为同学们开阔视野。同学们对出国留学的方方面面也有了更为清晰的认识，有助于更好地规划自己的未来发展方向。</FONT></SPAN></P>', 899, 1308823257, '2011-06-23 02:00:57', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(721, 10, '数学学院召开2010级本科生“科研实训”启动大会', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Calibri><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate w:st="on" IsROCDate="False" IsLunarDate="False" Day="21" Month="6" Year="2011"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>6</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>21</SPAN>日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">，数学学院在清水河校区<SPAN lang=EN-US>A213</SPAN>教室召开了<SPAN lang=EN-US>2010</SPAN>级本科生“科研实训”启动大会。高建副院长、张泽宝副书记、教务科科长、<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>级辅导员及<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>级全体同学参加了大会。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5" class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Calibri><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">首先，高建副院长为同学们解读了《</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">本科生“科研实训”的内容、规范和要求</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">》，介绍了<SPAN lang=EN-US>28</SPAN>、<SPAN lang=EN-US>29</SPAN>级科研训练的开展情况及部分成果，鼓励大家积极参与到研究训练中来，将</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">学习与研究相结合，<SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">在探索和研究的过程中</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">，<SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">训练基本研究能力和交流表达能力，培养创新意识与创新能力。随后，她</SPAN>向同学们详细介绍了“个人学习计划”，希望同学们根据自身的实际情况，明确发展方向和目标，有针对性的制定个人学习计划。</SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 15pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Calibri><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">最后，张泽宝副书记在讲话中指出，科研训练可以使同学们专业知识的学习更为扎实、专业技能更为娴熟，也有助于培养勇于探索创新的科学精神和严谨务实的科学态度，这对于同学们个人的成长具有重要的意义。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Calibri><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">会上，同学们对研究训练</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">表现出了极大的兴趣。会后，参加</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">研究训练的</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">报名工作将随后展开。</SPAN></FONT><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', 672, 1308878818, '2011-06-23 17:26:58', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `article` (`articleid`, `sortid`, `title`, `source`, `author`, `userid`, `content`, `click`, `publish_time`, `launch_time`, `imageid`, `keyword1`, `keyword2`, `keyword3`) VALUES
(722, 22, '“数科人在海外”第三期交流活动圆满成功', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=572"></FONT></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=571"></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri></FONT></SPAN></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>6</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>24</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">日下午</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2:30</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">，数学科学学院研究生科技文化活动——“数科人在海外”</SPAN><FONT face=Calibri> </FONT><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">留学交流沙龙第三期成功举办。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">本期交流会邀请到我院留学生唐可（现在美国东北大学商学院留学），在主楼</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>A1-512</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">与大家分享了游学美国的经历和感受。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">唐可幽默风趣的为同学们讲解了美国的概况、在美国的经历，然后对出国要提前准备的种种事项做了详尽的讲解。从</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>TOEFL、</FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>GRE、GMAT</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">等“硬件”准备到职业生涯规划等“软件</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">筹划，从在美国学习中困难的克服到日常生活中的乐趣等，都为学弟学妹们做了详尽的介绍。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><FONT size=3>虽然交流时间只有两个小时，但却让同学们充分的感受到了她游学美国中的酸甜苦辣，让同学们对出国留学、如何适应海外生活有了更加深层次的理解。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><FONT size=3>通过此类活动，学院整合各方面出国资源，营造留学氛围，多途径地为同学们开阔视野。使同学们更好地规划自己的未来发展方向。</FONT></SPAN></P>', 1050, 1308907301, '2011-06-24 01:21:41', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(723, 10, '我校学子勇夺第三届四川省ACM-ICPC大学生程序设计大赛冠军', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate w:st="on" IsROCDate="False" IsLunarDate="False" Day="26" Month="6" Year="2011"><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">6</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">月</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">26</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">日</SPAN></SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">下午，由四川省计算机学会主办的四川省第三届大学生</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; PADDING-LEFT: 0cm; PADDING-RIGHT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt; BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">ACM</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">程序设计大赛在成都东软学院落下帷幕。</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">我校派出</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">6</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">支代表队出战了此次比赛。经过五个小时的激烈拼搏，他们都发挥出了极高的水准。最终五支队伍获得一等奖，一支队伍获得二等奖。其中</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">UESTC_Obsidian</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">队，最终解出</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">7</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">题，夺得了本次比赛的桂冠。</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">四川省</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">ACM-ICPC</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">大学生程序设计大赛，历来被视作四川省规模最大、水平最高的大学生程序设计竞赛。川内各所高校都派出了最强的队伍参加了此次比赛，其中不乏刚刚参加第</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">35</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">届</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><FONT face="Times New Roman">ACM-ICPC</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">亚洲区区域赛和世界总决赛的队伍。</SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman "><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=573"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman "><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=574"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman "><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=575"></SPAN></SPAN></P><SPAN class=apple-style-span><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN>', 836, 1309755824, '2011-07-03 21:03:44', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
