om-alt: auto; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">注：<SPAN lang=EN-US>1.</SPAN>本表所列含税级距与不含税级距，均为按照税法规定减除有关费用后的所得额；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA" lang=EN-US>2.</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">含税级距适用于由纳税人负担税款的工资、薪金所得；不含税级距适用于由他人（单位）代付税款的工资、薪金所得。</SPAN>', 1460, 1315970566, '2011-09-13 19:22:46', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(881, 10, '数学学院2011-2012-2学期开学补考安排通知', '', NULL, 0, '<p>\r\n	<p class="detailTitle">\r\n		<span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-size:x-large;"><strong>数学学院&nbsp;2011-2012-2学期学院专业课开学补考通知</strong></span> </span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="detailTitle">\r\n		<span style="font-size:medium;"> <span style="font-size:large;">2011-2012-2学期学院专业课补考的具体时间地点请见附件，请要补考的同学注意查看考试时间地点，准时参加考试，并请相互转告。<span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;"><strong><span style="font-size:large;">考试时请务必带上准考证，学生凭准考证参加考试</span></strong>，<span style="font-size:large;">无</span></span></span><span style="font-size:large;"><strong><span style="font-family:宋体;color:red;font-size:12pt;">准考证</span></strong></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;"><span style="font-size:large;">不能参加考试。<br />\r\n另学校的补考安排请查看教务处首页或见网址：</span><a href="http://www.jwc.uestc.edu.cn/Index/Catalog57/3754.aspx"><span style="font-size:large;">http://www.jwc.uestc.edu.cn/Index/Catalog57/3754.aspx</span></a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:x-large;"> <strong>数学科学学院教务</strong></span></span></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="detailTitle">\r\n		<span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;"><span style="font-size:x-large;"><strong>附件<a href="/adminCotrol/editor/attached/file/20120302/20120302141649_25817.xls" target="_blank">补考安排表</a><br />\r\n</strong></span></span></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class="detailTitle">\r\n		<span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-size:12pt;"><span style="font-size:x-large;"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> </span></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</p>', 577, 1329897379, '2012-02-25 14:18:30', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
