(818, 11, '关于2011-2012学年助学金评定的通知', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">各同学：<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">为进一步做好家庭经济困难学生的资助工作，根据《普通本科高校、高等职业学校国家助学金管理暂行办法》精神，我校相应制定了《电子科技大学国家助学金管理办法》。现将<SPAN lang=EN-US>2011-2012</SPAN>学年助学金评选的相关事宜通知如下：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore"><FONT face="Times New Roman"><FONT size=3>1、</FONT><SPAN style="FONT: 7pt Times New Roman">&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">评定过程中要坚持公开、公平、公正的原则。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore"><FONT face="Times New Roman"><FONT size=3>2、</FONT><SPAN style="FONT: 7pt Times New Roman">&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">助学金分为国家助学金、专项助学金。国家助学金与专项助学金原则上不能兼得。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">3、</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">助学金具体申请条件及申请标准见附件。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">4、</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">日程具体安排如下：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 41.3pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 3.43" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>11</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>2-11</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>日</SPAN></B><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">根据《电子科技大学国家助学金管理办法》的规定开展助学金评定工作，并受理学生申请；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 23.6pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">5、<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt Times New Roman"> </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">学院初评，形成初评名单。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 41.8pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 3.47" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>11</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">月<SPAN lang=EN-US>8</SPAN>日<SPAN lang=EN-US>-11</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>9</SPAN>日<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">在适当范围公示两天，接受师生的异议并处理。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 23.6pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">所有申请同学根据班级评定情况下载助学金申请表，填写上交。</SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 23.6pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">班长根据评定情况下载助学金备案表，于11月8日前将电子档发送至辅导员邮箱。</SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 23.6pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">申请专项助学金的学生须向资助单位撰写感谢信和成长汇报，并与专项奖学金申请表一同报送（获安捷伦助学金资助学生感谢信需用英文撰写）</SPAN></B><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">说明：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">1、</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">在认定工作中优先考虑孤残学生、烈士子女、地震重灾区、少数民族家庭经济困难学生，以及家庭成员长期患重病、家庭遭遇自然灾害、或突发事件等特殊情况的学生。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">2、</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">申请助学金的学生必须是本学年申请并被认定为家庭经济困难的学生。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">3、</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">高额奖学金与高额助学金原则上不可兼得。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">4、</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">如评定为国家助学金无需报送申请表，如评定为专项助学金则需报送</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">申请表</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">附件<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>：电子科技大学国家助学金管理办法（试行）</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">附件2：电子科技大学助学金申请表</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">附件3：2011-2012年助学金名单备案表<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>', 539, 1320221547, '2011-11-02 00:12:27', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(819, 22, '2011-2012-1后10周学校所开的课程', '', NULL, 0, '<P>各位同学：</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 请查看2011-2012-1后10周学校所开的课程。</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 数学科学学院研究生科</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2011年11月4日</P>', 482, 1320392461, '2011-11-03 23:41:01', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(820, 10, '2010级 抽象代数 期中考试安排', '', NULL, 0, '<P><FONT size=5>2010级抽象代数期中考试定于2011年11月10日10:30-11:30在A206（2010101010班）、A207（2010101020班）、A211（2010102010班）</FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=5>A212（2010102020班）举行，请同学们相互转告。数学科学学院教务科</FONT></P>', 366, 1320650356, '2011-11-06 23:19:16', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(822, 10, '2009级数学物理方程期中考试安排', '', NULL, 0, '<FONT size=6>2009级数学物理方程期中考试定于2011年11月11日上午10:30-12:00在A102-数学与应用数学专业二个班、A103-29102010班、A105-29102020班举行，请同学们相互转告。数学科学学院教务科</FONT>', 409, 1320826666, '2011-11-09 00:17:46', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(823, 10, '大学生创新创业训练项目相关表格', '', NULL, 0, '详见附件！', 424, 1320976269, '2011-11-10 17:51:09', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `article` (`articleid`, `sortid`, `title`, `source`, `author`, `userid`, `content`, `click`, `publish_time`, `launch_time`, `imageid`, `keyword1`, `keyword2`, `keyword3`) VALUES
(824, 10, '数学学院开设研究性教学公开课', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Calibri><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">为不断深化研究性教学方法改革，提高课堂教学质量，培养创新型人才，数学科学学院于<SPAN lang=EN-US>11</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>日下午在清水河校区<SPAN lang=EN-US>A208</SPAN>教室举行了一次研究型教学公开课。黄廷祝院长、高建副院长、</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">院教学质量小组徐全智组长、</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">“线性代数”课程组全体教师以及学院的部分中青年教师参加了教学观摩。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face=Calibri>本次公开课由“线性代数”课程组的青年教师李厚彪老师主讲。李老师以“费马大定理的证明与启示”为引例介绍了科学研究的基本思想，将研究性教学理念贯穿于“行列式的古典定义与应用、分块矩阵行列式的计算与应用”等教学内容，信息量大、富于启发，课堂气氛活跃，学生积极主动，受到了教师与同学们的好评。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Calibri><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">此次活动作为</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">本学期数学学院教师培训计划之一，旨在推进研究性教学方法改革，促进教师之间交流教学经验、教学方法。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">活动由“线性代数”课程组主办。课后学院领导与课程组的全体老师就如何深入开展研究性教学方法改革作了广泛的交流与研讨。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>', 398, 1320976466, '2011-11-10 17:54:26', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(825, 10, '数学科学学院师生共话教学', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Calibri><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">为听取同学们对教学工作的意见，了解学生的学习状态，以加强教学管理，进一步提高教学质量。<SPAN lang=EN-US>11</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>日下午，数学学院在清水河校区召开了师生座谈会。高建副院长、张泽宝副书记、系主任、任课教师、各个年级的学生代表及教务科科长参加了此次座谈。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><FONT face=Calibri><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">会上，同学们畅所欲言，分别就教学管理、课堂教学、课程设置、学习方法、教师安排等同学们普遍关注的问题提出了自己的疑问或建议。学院领导和教师们认真听取了同学们的意见，就一些可现场解决的问题作了耐心细致的讲解；就需后续改进的方面作了详尽的记录，表示会进一步分析、研究这些问题，采纳合理的建议和意见并在工作中改进。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 20pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><FONT face=Calibri>最后，高建副院长表示，师生座谈会对于增进师生间的沟通、交流，完善教学管理、提高教学质量有着积极的作用。今后，还会继续保持畅通的沟通渠道，广泛听取同学们的建议和意见。同时，希望同学们发掘自身潜力，认真学习，刻苦钻研，力争成才！</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', 461, 1320976491, '2011-11-10 17:54:51', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(826, 11, '数学科学学院2011年“优班创建”答辩会成功召开', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>11</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>10</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">日下午</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>4:20</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">，数学科学学院</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">年优班创建答辩会在教学楼</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>A204</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">顺利召开。出席本次答辩会的嘉宾有学院党委孙清平书记、张泽宝副书记，辅导员叶谱英、李坤龙老师及助理辅导员许毅老师，答辩会由张娇老师主持。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">参加本次答辩会的各班代表和助威的同学们准时到达现场，答辩会正式开始前由来自</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri">个班级代表抽签决定各自出场顺序。本次答辩会分两个环节，第一为班级成果展示环节；第二为评委提问环节。各班代表身着正装，声情并茂地向各位评委老师及全体同学展示本班在学风建设、党团建设、寝室文化、社团实践等方面取得的各项优异成果，突显了班级的特色与文化。各评委老师分别就班级成果展现中的部分内容提出疑问，譬如“四级通过率”、“计算机等级考试”、出国留学等，各班级代表临场应变，为评委们一一作了解答。每一个班级答辩结束，现场都不约而同地传来同学们为自己班级加油助威的呐喊声，使得整场答辩会气氛尤其活跃。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><A name=_GoBack></A><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><FONT size=3>答辩会共历时近两个小时，最终诞生三个优秀班集体代表学院出席校级优秀班集体答辩。本次答辩会不仅全面展现了学院各班级在这一年来取得的优异成果，更使得各班级在成果展示过程中加深了对彼此的了解，增进了友谊，浓厚了情感。相信数科院的学子们能够在接下来的学习生活当中再接再厉，秉承学院的优良传统，全面发展，为学院与班级争得更加优异的成绩。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=648"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri"><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=649"></SPAN></P>', 563, 1320982728, '2011-11-10 19:38:48', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(827, 12, '北京大学章志飞教授学术讲座', '', NULL, 0, '<P>报告题目：Some recent results on the Navier-Stokes equations<BR>报&nbsp; 告&nbsp; 人：章志飞&nbsp; 教授<BR>报告地点：清水河校区主楼A1-512<BR>报告时间： 11月16日（周三）下午4：00</P>\r\n<P>报告人简介：章志飞，北京大学数学科学学院教授。主要从事流体动力学方程和Schrodinger方程等的调和分析方法研究，特别是在水波问题、Navier-Stokes方程以及Schrodinger方程等的研究上取得了突破，解决了多个公开问题。已在Comm. Pure Appl. Math. (2篇)、Adv. Math. (1篇)、Arch. Rational Mech. Anal. (3篇)，Comm. Math. Phys. (6篇)、J. Math. Pures Appl. (3篇)，Annales de l  Inst. Henri Poincare (1篇)，SIAM J. Math. Anal.(1篇)等顶尖学术期刊上发表学术论文30余篇。当前作为负责人承担了国家自然科学基金面上项目和作为主研人员参与国家自然科学基金重大项目各一项。</P>\r\n<P>报告摘要：In this talk, I will first review some known important&nbsp;results on the Navier-Stokes equations.&nbsp;Then I will talk about &nbsp;our &nbsp;recent results about the regularity of&nbsp;weak solution, weak-strong uniqueness, and&nbsp;global well-posedness for some classes of large initial data.</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>欢迎全校师生参加！</P>', 820, 1320994589, '2011-11-10 22:56:29', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(828, 9, '我院邀请电工学院教授做专业教育讲座', '', NULL, 0, '<SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 为进一步做好专业思想教育，使同学们加深对所学专业重要性的认知，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Calibri , sans-serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>11</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">月</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Calibri , sans-serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>10</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">日下午，学院专门邀请了我校知名专家、电子工程学院教授何子述老师为数理基科班和我院大一年级同学做讲座，黄廷祝院长出席并主持了讲座。</SPAN><FONT size=3 face=宋体> </FONT>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p><FONT face=Calibri>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 何教授重点讲述了数学与电子信息工程的关系问题，引导广大同学学好自身专业，为将来选择研究方向做好准备。他</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">强调，所有的工程科学都是以数学为基础，这是全世界公认的，大多数的工程问题都是需要数学描述，如果离开数学寸步难行。何教授一连举了几个例子例证数学对于电子工程的重要性，利用上网、电话、短信等日常的小事，为同学们讲述了二进制数如何传输，这涉及到复杂的数学描述、处理，并通过展示雷达图片，用公式说话，说明通信的信道均衡，卡尔曼滤波与雷达目标跟踪等都需要数学知识完成轨迹的计算，随机过程预测等。</SPAN><FONT size=3 face=宋体> </FONT>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face=Calibri>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Calibri , sans-serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">何教授谈到，数学功力决定了一个人学术水平的高低，数学水平是决定成为工匠还是学者的重要因素，同时他还告诉同学们信号处理越来越软件化，鼓励同学们选择电子信息作为未来的相关研究方向。</SPAN><FONT size=3 face=宋体> </FONT>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face=Calibri>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face=Calibri>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </FONT></o:p></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">在互动环节，同学们踊跃发言提问，何教授、黄院长都耐心地予以了解答。讲座结束后，同学们纷纷表示，希望学院今后多举办一些这样的讲座，让同学们多接触一些相关方面的信息，进一步加深对学好本专业重要性的认识。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Calibri , sans-serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Calibri , sans-serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=650"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Calibri , sans-serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=652"></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT face=Calibri>&nbsp;<IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=651"></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>', 551, 1321000661, '2011-11-11 00:37:41', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(830, 9, '中科院石钟慈院士做客成电讲坛', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>11</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>15</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">日下午，中科院石钟慈院士做客成电讲坛，向同学们阐释了自己求学、治学、教学的“成长之路”。此次讲坛由校党委学生工作部主办、数学科学学院承办。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=654" width=486 height=311></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=655" width=488 height=299></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=653" width=487 height=298></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">清水河图书馆二楼</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>600</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">人报告厅座无虚席，很多同学站着听完整场讲座。主持人简单介绍了石院士的基本事迹，拉开本次演讲的序幕。在一<A name=_GoBack></A>片热烈的掌声中，石钟慈院士以自己求学、治学、教学生涯为主线深情回顾了过去几十年成长的点点滴滴。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">石院士生于上世纪</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>30</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">年代，自小在农村长大，家家户户年轻人背井离乡远去上海打工挣钱的风气并未动摇石院士自主求学的决心，从乡下初中考入县里高中，再到浙江大学数学系，之后又远赴俄国主修计算数学。学成归国在中国科技大学任教，同时担任中科院院士和著名数学杂志的主编。回首一生，石院士难忘师恩，不论是高中的数学启蒙老师，还是大学时代的导师</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>----</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">华罗庚先生，都深刻影响着石院士的人生轨迹和精神世界。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><FONT size=3>石院士还亲切教导我们做人不可过分的张扬骄傲，要时时刻刻保持谦虚的品德。既然选择了科学的道路，就必须耐得住寂寞，在科学殿堂孜孜以求。朴素的言语，真实的经历，石院士的演讲给每一个认真聆听的学子以深深地启迪和教育，相信参加本次讲座的科大学子之中，会有越来越多向石钟慈院士一样勤奋修学、谦虚质朴的英才。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p><FONT size=3 face=Calibri>&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">相关链接：</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">石钟慈，男，浙江宁波人，数学家。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1991</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">年当选为中国科学院院士。现任中国计算数学学会理事长，是我国计算数学领域四个刊物的主编；德国、美国、俄罗斯、日本和巴西五个国际计算数学杂志的编委。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1933</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">月生于浙江宁波，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1955</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">年毕业于复旦大学数学系，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1956</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">年赴苏联科学院</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>Steklov</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">数学研究所攻读计算数学。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1960</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">年到中国科学院计算所工作。曾任中国科技大学数学系主任、中国科学院计算中心主任。曾获中科院重大科技成果二等奖，科技进步一等奖，国家自然科学三等奖、华罗庚数学奖和何梁何利科技进步奖。曾任国家攀登计划项目首席科学家。</SPAN></P>', 601, 1321429443, '2011-11-15 23:44:03', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(835, 13, '关于开展第二批校“百人计划”申报的通知!', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">根据《</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">电子科技大学“百人计划”实施办法</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">》，现就开展第二批校“百人计划”申报工作的有关事项通知如下。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 6pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class=MsoNormal align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">一、申报条件</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0.1pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt -0.1pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-left: -.01gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-outline-level: 2" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（一）具有博士学位，一般不超过<SPAN lang=EN-US>40</SPAN>岁；</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Verdana , sans-serif ; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -35.45pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 40.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-outline-level: 2" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（二）具有良好的个人品德，健康向上的心理素质，严谨求实的学术作风，较强的团队组织领导能力和拼搏奉献精神；</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Verdana , sans-serif ; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -35.55pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 40.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-outline-level: 2" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（三）能够把握本学科的发展方向，具有前瞻性、创新性的学术构想，在学科领域内具有较高的学术影响力，学术成果得到广泛认可；</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Verdana , sans-serif ; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -35.4pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 40.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-outline-level: 2" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">（四）具备在“百人计划”岗位聘期内入选“长江学者”奖励计划或获得“国家杰出青年科学基金”的潜力。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Verdana , sans-serif ; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 6pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class=MsoNormal align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">二、</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">申报材料</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">申报人应认真、如实填写《电子科技大学百人计划候选人推荐表》（见附件），不得空项、漏项，各推荐单位对申报材料应严格审核、把关。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 6pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm" class=MsoNormal align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">三、</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">时间安排</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">请各单位于<B><SPAN lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>11</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>25</SPAN>日</B>之前将《电子科技大学百人计划候选人推荐表》纸质档提交到人事处人才工作办公室（清水河校区主楼<SPAN lang=EN-US>B2-501</SPAN>室，沙河校区主楼中<SPAN lang=EN-US>240</SPAN>室），电子档发送至</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><A href="mailto:jinggao@uestc.edu.cn"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">jinggao@uestc.edu.cn</SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">联系人：高晶<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><A href="mailto:jinggao@uestc.edu.cn"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">jinggao@uestc.edu.cn</SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>028-61830504</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 72pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 6.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">李敏<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><A href="mailto:limin@uestc.edu.cn"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">limin@uestc.edu.cn</SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>028-61830385</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">附件：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><A href="http://www.pd.uestc.edu.cn/content4.asp?s_type=down&amp;fid=15&amp;id=420"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><SPAN lang=EN-US>电子科技大学百人计划候选人推荐表</SPAN></SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', 555, 1321601565, '2011-11-17 23:32:45', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(836, 10, '创新项目申报', '', NULL, 0, '<P><FONT size=6>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 项目收集随时更新，请随时关注。请同学们抓紧时间在下星期三之前完成申报！<FONT color=#cc3333>纸质档和电子档同时交！</FONT>请相互转告。</FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT size=6>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;数学学院教务科</FONT></P>', 1141, 1321601638, '2011-11-17 23:33:58', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(837, 11, '数学学院敬老院献爱心活动', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 11</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>19</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">日下午，数学科学学院</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>10</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">级党支部和</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>maple</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">志愿者服务队一行</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>40</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">多人在成都颐乐村敬老院开展了“敬老爱老献爱心”活动。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=center><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=656"></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal> </SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=center><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=658"></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=center><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=657"></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><FONT size=3>星期六下午，阳光明媚，参加活动的同学们来到位于金牛区跃进村的颐乐村敬老院。本次活动分为三个环节：第一环节由各位同学给敬老院的每位老人送上礼品，表达自己的一份爱心和关怀；第二环节是打扫卫生，同学们手持卫生工具，清扫院子，擦洗桌椅，忙得不亦乐乎；最重要的环节是和颐乐村敬老院建立了长期合作关系，并且在敬老院挂牌，成立数学科学学院志愿服务基地，为老人们长期志愿服务，献一份年轻人的爱心！</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><FONT size=3>虽然已经是冬天，但是同学们的额头上还是出现了汗珠。打扫完毕后，同学们又分成小组，和每位老人聊家常，给老人讲故事，耐心听老人对我们的教导。老人们的脸上都浮现出笑容。最后，同学们轮流给老人表演精彩的节目，引来了老人们的阵阵掌声。天色渐暗，一张活动合影给此次活动画上了圆满的句号。</FONT></SPAN></P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri , sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">此次活动给老人们带去了同学们的爱心和祝福，让老人们感受到了社会大家庭的温暖，看到了社会未来的希望。参加活动的同学们也表示通过这次活动，更加增强了尊老爱老的意识，同时也增加了同学们的社会责任感。</SPAN> ', 638, 1321845325, '2011-11-20 19:15:25', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `article` (`articleid`, `sortid`, `title`, `source`, `author`, `userid`, `content`, `click`, `publish_time`, `launch_time`, `imageid`, `keyword1`, `keyword2`, `keyword3`) VALUES
(843, 9, '两硕士论文荣获2011年四川省优秀硕士学位论文奖', '', NULL, 0, '<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Arial; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt"><FONT size=3></FONT></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: #666666; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"> </SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">根据川学位【</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">】</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">28</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">号文件四川省教育厅</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">四川省人民政府学位委员会关于批准</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">年四川省优秀硕士学位论文的决定，我学院两位毕业生获得</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">年四川省优秀硕士学位论文奖。此次四川省优秀硕士学位论文奖</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">,</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">我校共有</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">39</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">人获得。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">我院获</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">年四川省优秀硕士学位论文奖的为</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">2006</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">级计算数学专业两位硕士毕业生：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 20pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> <o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<DIV align=center>\r\n<TABLE class=MsoNormalTable style="BORDER-RIGHT: medium none; BORDER-TOP: medium