TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-alt: 9.15pt" align=center><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">白玉琴</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman"> <SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P></TD>\r\n<TD style="BORDER-RIGHT: black 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: #ebe9ed; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: #ebe9ed; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1pt solid; HEIGHT: 9.15pt; BACKGROUND-COLOR: transparent; mso-border-left-alt: solid black 1.0pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid black 1.0pt" vAlign=top>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-alt: 9.15pt" align=center><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">黄廷祝</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></DIV>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" align=left><FONT size=3><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: black">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: #666666; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">评选四川省优秀硕士学位论文，是贯彻落实《四川省中长期教育改革和发展规划纲要（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">2010-2020</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">）》，提高研究生培养质量，鼓励创新，促进高层次创造性人才脱颖而出的重要措施。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>', 587, 1322187632, '2011-11-24 18:20:32', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(839, 9, '我校学子在第三届全国大学生数学竞赛四川赛区赛中再获佳绩', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">由中国数学会主办的第三届全国大学生数学竞赛四川赛区赛于</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">年</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>10</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">月</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>29</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">日在</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">四川大学</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">举行。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">包括四川大学、电子科技大学、西南交通大学在内的</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">省内各院校</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">参加</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">了竞赛。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 20.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.71" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">我校学生在</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">本次</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">竞赛</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">中取得</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">优异成绩。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">在</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">非</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">数学类专业</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">类</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">中，</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">我校学生包揽前<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>名，取得参加全国决赛<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>个名额中的<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>个，一等奖获奖数占全省的</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>44.4%</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">，参赛学生获奖比例为</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>51</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>%</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">，</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">位于所有参赛学校之首；</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">在数学类专业</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">类</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">中，</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">获奖情况位居全省第二，</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">参赛学生获奖比例为</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>72.7%</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class=MsoNormal><FONT face="Times New Roman"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">全国大学生数学竞赛是由中国数学会</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">年开始举行的全国性数学竞赛，每年举办一次。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">竞赛分为数学专业类和非数学专业类，参赛对象为大学本科二年级及以上在校大学生，竞赛内容以本科教学大纲规定的数学内容为准，比赛形式采用纸质试卷笔试，竞赛分为省区比赛和全国决赛两个阶段。</SPAN></FONT><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', 552, 1322100609, '2011-11-23 18:10:09', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(840, 22, '2010级研究生开题报告的有关安排', '', NULL, 0, '<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">根据硕士生培养方案要求，<SPAN lang=EN-US>2010</SPAN>级硕士生已完成课程学习，进入开题报告阶段。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">现将<SPAN lang=EN-US>2010</SPAN>级研究生开题报告的有关安排通知如下：</SPAN></P><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、<B>开题报告材料：</B></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><STRONG>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </STRONG>其中包括《开题报告表》和《文献综述》。《开题报告表》和《文献综述封面》的模板见附件（请严格按照规范填写，双面打印）<B>《文献综述》要求：</B>文献综述须引用本学科前沿国内外文献<SPAN lang=EN-US>20</SPAN>篇以上，外文文献<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>篇以上，报告内容不少于<SPAN lang=EN-US>4000</SPAN>字，并附上不小于<SPAN lang=EN-US>1000</SPAN>字的英文详细摘要；报告中应提出值得研究和解决的学术或技术问题，并在此基础上完成相应的开题报告。<SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">《开题报告表》纸质版须由专家组签署意见后交到学院研究生科。《文献综述》由导师签署意见后交到学院研究生科。</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">请各位同学按期提交开题，分组信息及时间、地点安排请见附件，过期将不再受理，延迟提交会直接影响答辩，请各位同学相互转告。（请提前到达开题的地点：装入PPT）</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bid