(841, 22, '三位博士生获2011年中央高校基本科研业务费——优秀博士生支持计划项目立项', '', NULL, 0, '<SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 根据《中央高校基本科研业务费——优秀博士生支持计划项目管理办法（试行）》的相关要求，经博士生申请，专家评审后，学校决定对我院何军（导师：黄廷祝教授）、田俊康（导师：钟守铭教授）、江婧（导师：舒兰教授）三位博士生申报的课题给予立项资助。</SPAN>', 724, 1322124512, '2011-11-24 00:48:32', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(842, 12, '四位青年教师获2011年中央高校基本科研业务费项目立项', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">根据《电子科技大学关于</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">年度中央高校基本科研业务费立项的通知》文件，我院</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">四位青年教师获</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">2011</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">年中央高校基本科研业务费项目立项资助：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">新兴与交叉项目</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">项：荆燕飞</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">基础研究项目</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">项：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ">段勇、吴磊、邓志亮</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">截止到目前，我院一共获批中央高校基本科研业务费项目</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">21</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">项，其中基础研究项目</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">18</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">项，新兴与交叉项目</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">项，经费总计</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">98.5</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt">万元。</SPAN>', 765, 1322124545, '2011-11-24 00:49:05', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(846, 22, '关于通知学生提前核对网上学籍信息的重要通知', '', NULL, 0, '<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋">为保证我校发放的研究生学位证书中所涉及学生本人的相关信息内容正确无误，如姓名、性别、出生日期等，保证学位证书发放过程严肃、规范、准确。研究生院特作出以下规定：<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 57.25pt; TEXT-INDENT: -29.25pt; tab-stops: list 57.25pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 华文仿宋"><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">1.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt  Times New Roman ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋">新生入学第一学期要完成网上个人学籍信息核对工作，在读期间如有变更应及时更正。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 57.25pt; TEXT-INDENT: -29.25pt; tab-stops: list 57.25pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 华文仿宋"><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">2.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt  Times New Roman ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋">高年级研究生应在申请答辩前一学期完成网上个人学籍信息核对工作。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 57.25pt; TEXT-INDENT: -29.25pt; tab-stops: list 57.25pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 华文仿宋"><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">3.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt  Times New Roman ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋">对于本学期申请答辩的研究生，应在<SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>月开分委会之前完成网上个人学籍信息核对工作</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋">。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 57.25pt; TEXT-INDENT: -29.25pt; tab-stops: list 57.25pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋; mso-bidi-font-family: 华文仿宋"><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">4.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt  Times New Roman ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋">每年<SPAN lang=EN-US>6</SPAN>月及<SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>月份，学位办将按时完成授位研究生的学位证书制作工作。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋">从<SPAN lang=EN-US>2011</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>月起，研究生院学位办在打印学位证书前将默认网上学生的学籍信息无误，以后将不再受理因学生个人信息有误而更换其学位证书的申请。如果因证书制作质量问题可到学位办申请更换，申请时间为领取证书一周内。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋">请各学院将以上规定通知到每一位研究生同学，并督促其核对网上个人信息。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21pt; TEXT-ALIGN: right" align=right><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21pt; TEXT-ALIGN: right" align=right><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋">电子科技大学研究生院学位办<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21pt; TEXT-ALIGN: right" align=right><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate w:st="on" Year="2011" Month="12" Day="1" IsLunarDate="False" IsROCDate="False"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋">2011</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋">年<SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>日</SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 华文仿宋"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', 524, 1322721584, '2011-11-30 22:39:44', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(847, 11, '何子述教授为我院学生做专题讲座', '', NULL, 0, '<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">日下午，我院邀请电工学院何子述教授在教学楼</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>B403</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">为</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>09</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>10</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">级同学们做专业知识和人生发展讲座，院党委张泽宝副书记、分团委书记李坤龙老师出席了本次讲座。</SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=661" align=baseline border=0></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=662" align=baseline border=0></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><FONT size=3>讲座开始之前，同学们提前到场等待何教授，并以热烈的掌声欢迎他的到来。在正式宣讲前，何教授做了简单的自我介绍，并感谢数学学院的热情邀请。在本次讲座中何教授主要就信号处理等方面的数学运用为同学了做了有力引导，通过举例应用的方式启迪同学们在数学领域的科学思维。何教授说数学是工程科学的基础，只有学好数学，才能往更高更深层次发展。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><FONT size=3>本次讲座使同学们在信号处理方面有了更深层次认识，在掌握数学专业知识的同时，了解到了最新的工程技术项目，在以后的职业选择中将起到重大作用，相信大家都获益匪浅。</FONT></SPAN></P>', 496, 1322811435, '2011-12-01 23:37:15', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
INSERT INTO `article` (`articleid`, `sortid`, `title`, `source`, `author`, `userid`, `content`, `click`, `publish_time`, `launch_time`, `imageid`, `keyword1`, `keyword2`, `keyword3`) VALUES
(848, 11, '“关注社会、践行责任”暑期社会实践交流会圆满举办', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>1</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">日，数学科学学院在教学楼</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>A212</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">室举行了</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">年主题团日活动</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>--</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">暑期社会实践经验交流会，向</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>11</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">级新生们展示了</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">年学院暑期社会实践的优秀成果。我院分团委书记李坤龙老师、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>11</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">级辅导员叶谱英老师和全体</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>11</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">级新生参加了本次交流会。</SPAN></FONT></P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">首先李老师发表讲话，总结了我院</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>2011</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">年暑假社会实践取得的优异成果。今年暑期社会实践我院实践团队共获得三等奖两个和优胜奖一个，共有</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>28</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">位同学获得暑期社会实践优秀个人。随后，暑期实践的获奖代表讲述了各自在暑期社会实践中难忘的经历，都江堰团队体验了农民生活的艰辛，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=Calibri>maple</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">志愿者和红铅笔团队感受到大山孩子对知识的渴望，台湾交流同学分享了宝岛的风土人情，晴空工作室同学们倍感程序设计的艰辛等等，各自展现了暑期社会实践的丰硕收获。</SPAN></FONT></P><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><FONT size=3>交流会结束后，大家都有意犹未尽的感觉，学长们分享的暑期实践经历让同学们受益匪浅，不少同学上前咨询，想了解更多各类暑期实践活动的情况，展现了极大地热情，想要迫切参与到实践活动的行列中，收获一段难得的经历和体验，更好地关注社会、融入社会，并贡献自己的一份绵薄之力</FONT><A name=_GoBack></A><FONT size=3>。</FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><FONT size=3><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=663"></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><FONT size=3><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=664"></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><FONT size=3><IMG border=0 hspace=0 alt="" align=baseline src="http://www.math.uestc.edu.cn//showimg.php?iid=665"></FONT></SPAN></P></SPAN></SPAN>', 366, 1322811750, '2011-12-01 23:42:30', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(849, 22, '电子科技大学研究生学籍信息更改管理办法', '', NULL, 0, '<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">各学院：<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">为了严肃研究生学籍管理工作，保证研究生学籍信息的准确性，对研究生入学后学籍信息的更改做出如下规定：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">一、关键个人信息更改（姓名、身份证号）<SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>1</SPAN>、学生本人持以下申请材料到研招办：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">（<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>）更改姓名：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">①《电子科大在校研究生学籍基本信息变更申请表》（一式两份）；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">②身份证原件及复印件；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">③学生证原件及复印件；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">④加盖公安机关公章的户口复印件，并贴本人近期一寸彩色照片。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">（<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>）更改身份证号码：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">①上述“更改姓名”中提及的全部材料；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">②公安机关出具的《公民身份号码更正证明》原件及加盖公章的复印件（个人填写错误的不需此材料）。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">2</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">、研招办对比录取信息签署意见并盖章，修改录取库信息，复印申请材料存档。<SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>3</SPAN>、研究生院学生管理科修改学生信息，申请材料原件存档。<SPAN lang=EN-US><BR></SPAN>二、非关键个人信息更改<SPAN lang=EN-US><BR><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN>学生本人持《电子科大在校研究生学籍基本信息变更申请表》（一式两份）及相关证明到研究生院学生管理科，经审核同意后更改，申请材料原件存档。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">三、证书编号（如：毕业证书编号、学位证书编号等）不能更改。<SPAN lang=EN-US><BR></SPAN>四、录取专业不能更改。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">五、录取类别更改<SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>1</SPAN>、录取类别只能由自筹改为委培，不得由委培改为自筹。<SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>2</SPAN>、学生本人持以下申请材料到研招办：<SPAN lang=EN-US><BR></SPAN>①本人书面申请；<SPAN lang=EN-US><BR></SPAN>②已签字盖章的委培协议书一式三份。<SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>3</SPAN>、研招办对比录取信息签署意见并盖章，修改录取库信息，复印申请材料存档，委培协议书一份存档。<SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>4</SPAN>、研究生院学生管理科修改学生信息，申请材料原件存档。<SPAN lang=EN-US><BR>5</SPAN>、学院凭委培协议书认可更改成功。<SPAN lang=EN-US><BR></SPAN>六、录取导师更改<SPAN lang=EN-US><BR><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN>学生在研究生院网站下载填写《电子科技大学博士<SPAN lang=EN-US>/</SPAN>硕士研究生转换导师申请表》，然后到研究生院学位科申请办理。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 28.1pt; TEXT-INDENT: -28.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: -2.0"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 28.1pt; TEXT-INDENT: -28.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: -2.0"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 28.1pt; TEXT-INDENT: -28.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: -2.0"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 28.1pt; TEXT-INDENT: -28.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: -2.0"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">研究生院<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 28.1pt; TEXT-INDENT: -28.1pt; mso-char-indent-count: -2.0"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">二０一０年五月十日<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>', 460, 1323051576, '2011-12-04 18:19:36', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(850, 11, '2011年数学科学学院年度人物评选工作启动', '', NULL, 0, '&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2011年数学科学学院年度人物评选拉开序幕，此项活动集中展示每年我院学子风采并营造多元化发展的氛围，评选方案见附件1，今年的评选工作安排如下：<BR>&nbsp; 1.12月5日——11日，申请阶段，个人或团队以自荐或他荐的方式按照方案中要求上报完整的申请材料；<BR>&nbsp; 2.12月12日——14日，初评阶段，学院根据申报者材料进行审核并确定初选名单；<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;3.12月15日——18日，公示&amp;网投阶段，在学院网上专栏展示初选者事迹，接受公众投票，网上投票率将作为终审的重要参考；<BR>&nbsp; 4.12月19日——21日，终审阶段，结合申请人材料、公示情况及投票结果，确定最终人选，并在12月23日学院年终表彰晚会上颁奖。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 数学科学学院学生科<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2011年12月5日</P>', 732, 1323054684, '2011-12-04 19:11:24', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL);
