(855, 9, '我院再次获高校博士点专项科研基金博导类项目', '', NULL, 0, '<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">近日，据教育部科技发展中心公布信息，我院黄廷祝教授再次获高等学校博士学科点专项科研基金博导类项目资助。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">项目名称：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>Markov</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">链问题的高性能算法研究</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">经费：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>12</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">万</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">这是我院继</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>2007</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">年第一次获得此类项目之后，再次获得博士点基金博导类项目。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">据知，本年度博士点基金博导类项目我校共获批</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>10</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">项。另外，本年度的优先发展领域类项目、新教师类项目我校分别获批</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">项和</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US>12</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">项。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY:  Times New Roman , serif ; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', 502, 1323413441, '2011-12-08 22:50:41', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL),
