(878, 22, '关于数学科学学院2009级硕士研究生论文答辩安排的通知', '', NULL, 0, '<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=center><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">关于数学科学学院<SPAN lang=EN-US>2009</SPAN>级硕士研究生论文答辩安排的通知</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">一、硕士学位论文的基本要求</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、学位论文的选题应有一定的理论意义与学术价值，应有必要的理论分析与实验结果，并有新的见解；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、学位论文应表明作者在本学科掌握了坚实的基础理论和系统的专门知识，具有从事科学研究工作或独立担负专门技术工作的能力；<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、硕士学位论文应是在导师的指导下，由硕士生独立完成的成果，多人合作的课题应明确区分本人所做的工作，共同部分应加以说明。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">二、硕士学位论文工作</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">硕士生在导师指导下确定选题后，进入学位论文工作，其时间一般不少于一年。论文工作期间应每月一次向导师汇报研究进展情况，按时完成相应的工作。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">三、学位论文的撰写</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、学位论文的撰写，应在导师的指导下，由硕士研究生独立完成。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、硕士研究生用于论文研究和撰写学位论文工作的时间不得少于一年。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、硕士学位论文的撰写要求概念清楚，分析严谨，条理分明，文字图表清晰。、<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、论文初稿须经导师审阅批准后方可付印，并按照《研究生学位论文撰写格式规范》撰写与装订。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">四、答辩申请及要求</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">工学硕士研究生必须完成培养方案中规定的所有环节，成绩合格，并获得导师同意后方可申请参加学位论文答辩。提交申请时须提交以下材料：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (1)&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">教学实践表<SPAN lang=EN-US>(</SPAN>三选一<SPAN lang=EN-US>)</SPAN>：主要指面向本科生的教学工作，如部分授课、辅导答疑、批改作业、指导毕业设计等。工作量不少于<SPAN lang=EN-US>40</SPAN>学时，由导师给出评语，学院给予书面证明，完成工作量后给予<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>学分。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (2)&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">社会实践<SPAN lang=EN-US>(</SPAN>三选一<SPAN lang=EN-US>)</SPAN>：主要是指研究生运用所学知识到科研院所、企事业单位等进行社会调查，参与一些工程项目，并写出总结报告，完成后给予<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>学分。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (3)&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">素质教育校公选课<SPAN lang=EN-US>(</SPAN>三选一<SPAN lang=EN-US>)</SPAN>：主要为加强研究生综合素质教育，研究生可选修一门，通过后获得<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>个学分。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(4)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">学术活动表：参加校内外学术活动至少<SPAN lang=EN-US>10</SPAN>次完成后给予<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>学分，须导师签字。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (5)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">答辩申请表<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">同时，申请答辩前须交清全部学费。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">五、</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">答辩前须提交的材料时间及要求</SPAN></B><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><FONT face="Times New Roman">1.</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">交申请表时到研究生科录取答辩袋，并按照袋内相关表格填写内容，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">要求书写工整。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、如有发表的论文请到研究生科进行登记。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、论文两本<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;(1)&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">提交的两本论文初稿不用去文印中心正式装订，只需打印后自行简易装册，需双面打印，并由导师在封面上签字。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">(2)&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">学院将对论文进行格式审查，对格式不符合要求的，将不予授理。请参加答辩研究生同学在做论文时一定严格按照《研究生学位论文撰写格式规范》要求，严格把好论文格式质量关。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;(2)&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">论文评阅通过后，本人按评阅专家意见修改后须提交文印中心正式装订论文五本。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、毕业生登记表（须贴照片）：交答辩申请书时到研管科领取。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">六、涉密研究生论文答辩</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">按照《电子科技大学涉密会议保密管理规定》中的相关条例办理。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、涉密论文须填写“电子科大涉密研究生论文定密审查程序表”，并在学院研管科办理相关手续后，方可到文印中心打印装订论文<SPAN lang=EN-US> (</SPAN>注：在提交答辩申请时所确定密级不得更改<SPAN lang=EN-US>)</SPAN>。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、“电子科大涉密研究生论文定密审查程序表”<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">七、关于论文查重的要求</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=ListParagraph style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18.75pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family:  Times New Roman "><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore"><FONT face="Times New Roman">1.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt  Times New Roman ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">研究生（博士生、硕士生）正式提交电子档论文后，将使用《学位论文学术不端行为检测系统》（以下简称“检测系统”）进行查重。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=ListParagraph style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18.75pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family:  Times New Roman "><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore"><FONT face="Times New Roman">2.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt  Times New Roman ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">首次查重结果，硕士研究生总体查重比率须低于</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">20%(</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">包括</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">20%),</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">并且各章节的查重比率不超过</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">40%</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">（含</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">40%</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">）方可参加答辩。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=ListParagraph style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18.75pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family:  Times New Roman "><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore"><FONT face="Times New Roman">3.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt  Times New Roman ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">硕士研究生首次总体查重率超过</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">20%</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">或单章超过</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">40%,</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">而总体查重率低于</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">40%(</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">包括</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">40%),</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">需经学院、导师的同意，在规定时间内进行二次修改（要求修改时间为一个月以上）并经检测系统二次查重后符合上一条要求，才可参加答辩。二次查重后若仍不符合要求，半年内将不再受理答辩。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=ListParagraph style="MARGIN: 0cm 10.3pt 0pt 0cm; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-right: .98gd"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">注：如果检测系统收费，二次查重费用由研究生自行承担。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=ListParagraph style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18.75pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family:  Times New Roman "><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore"><FONT face="Times New Roman">4.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt  Times New Roman ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">首次查重率超过</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">40%</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">，半年内将不再受理答辩；若已获学位，事后超过此查重比率（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">40%</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">），将取消研究生获得的学位。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=ListParagraph style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18.75pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family:  Times New Roman "><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore"><FONT face="Times New Roman">5.<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt  Times New Roman ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">申报校优秀硕士学位论文的查重率须低于</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><FONT face="Times New Roman">15%</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">，另外，学院将不对提交论文进行预查重检测，论文经正式一次性提交检测系统检测后，将根据该次检测结果执行上述办法。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;</SPAN><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">八、论文答辩受理时间（</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:  Times New Roman ; mso-hansi-font-family:  Times New Roman ">根据学生的论文情况进行调整，相对集中答辩）。</SPAN><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #686b60; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left; ms